lerange-2"><code>clearLiveSeekableRange</code></a>();</span><span data-idl=
=3D"" class=3D"idlMethod" id=3D"idl-def-mediasource-istypesupported-type" d=
ata-title=3D"isTypeSupported" data-dfn-for=3D"MediaSource">
    static<span class=3D"idlType"> <a data-link-type=3D"interface" href=3D"=
https://webidl.spec.whatwg.org/#idl-boolean">boolean</a></span> <a class=3D=
"internalDFN idlName" data-link-type=3D"method" href=3D"https://w3c.github.=
io/media-source/#dom-mediasource-istypesupported" id=3D"ref-for-dom-mediaso=
urce-istypesupported-1"><code>isTypeSupported</code></a>(<span class=3D"idl=
Type"><a data-link-type=3D"interface" href=3D"https://webidl.spec.whatwg.or=
g/#idl-DOMString">DOMString</a></span> <span class=3D"idlParamName">type</s=
pan>);</span>
};</span></code></pre>
      <section id=3D"handle-attribute"><div class=3D"header-wrapper"><h3 id=
=3D"x3-1-handle-attribute"><bdi class=3D"secno">3.1 </bdi>
        <dfn data-export=3D"" data-dfn-type=3D"attribute" id=3D"dom-mediaso=
urce-handle" data-idl=3D"attribute" data-title=3D"handle" data-dfn-for=3D"M=
ediaSource" data-type=3D"MediaSourceHandle" data-lt=3D"handle" data-local-l=
t=3D"MediaSource.handle" tabindex=3D"0" aria-haspopup=3D"dialog"><code>hand=
le</code></dfn> attribute
      </h3><a class=3D"self-link" href=3D"https://w3c.github.io/media-sourc=
e/#handle-attribute" aria-label=3D"Permalink for Section 3.1"></a></div>
      <p>
        Contains a handle useful for attachment of a dedicated worker <a da=
ta-link-type=3D"idl" data-lt=3D"MediaSource" href=3D"https://w3c.github.io/=
media-source/#dom-mediasource" class=3D"internalDFN" id=3D"ref-for-dom-medi=
asource-19"><code>MediaSource</code></a> object to an
        <a data-link-type=3D"interface" data-lt=3D"HTMLMediaElement" href=
=3D"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/media.html#htmlmediaelement"><co=
de>HTMLMediaElement</code></a> via <a data-link-type=3D"attribute" href=3D"=
https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/media.html#dom-media-srcobject"><cod=
e>srcObject</code></a>. The handle remains the same object
        for this <a data-link-type=3D"idl" data-lt=3D"MediaSource" href=3D"=
https://w3c.github.io/media-source/#dom-mediasource" class=3D"internalDFN" =
id=3D"ref-for-dom-mediasource-20"><code>MediaSource</code></a> object acros=
s accesses of this attribute, but it is distinct for
        each <a data-link-type=3D"idl" data-lt=3D"MediaSource" href=3D"http=
s://w3c.github.io/media-source/#dom-mediasource" class=3D"internalDFN" id=
=3D"ref-for-dom-mediasource-21"><code>MediaSource</code></a> object.
      </p>
      <div class=3D"note" role=3D"note" id=3D"issue-container-generatedID-5=
"><div role=3D"heading" class=3D"note-title marker" id=3D"h-note-5" aria-le=
vel=3D"3"><span>Note</span></div><p class=3D"">
        This specification may eventually enable visibility of this attribu=
te on <a data-link-type=3D"idl" data-lt=3D"MediaSource" href=3D"https://w3c=
.github.io/media-source/#dom-mediasource" class=3D"internalDFN" id=3D"ref-f=
or-dom-mediasource-22"><code>MediaSource</code></a>
        objects on the main Window context. If so, specification care will =
be necessary to prevent
        potential backwards incompatible changes, such as could happen if e=
xceptions were thrown on
        accesses to this attribute.
      </p></div>
      <p>
        On getting, run the following steps:
      </p>
      <ol>
        <li>If the handle for this <a data-link-type=3D"idl" data-lt=3D"Med=
iaSource" href=3D"https://w3c.github.io/media-source/#dom-mediasource" clas=
s=3D"internalDFN" id=3D"ref-for-dom-mediasource-23"><code>MediaSource</code=
></a> object has not yet been created, then run the
        following steps:
          <ol>
            <li>Let <var data-type=3D"MediaSourceHandle">created handle</va=
r> be the result of creating a new
            <a data-link-type=3D"idl" data-lt=3D"MediaSourceHandle" href=3D=
"https://w3c.github.io/media-source/#dom-mediasourcehandle" class=3D"intern=
alDFN" id=3D"ref-for-dom-mediasourcehandle-3"><code>MediaSourceHandle</code=
></a> object and associated resources, linked internally to this
            <a data-link-type=3D"idl" data-lt=3D"MediaSource" href=3D"https=
://w3c.github.io/media-source/#dom-mediasource" class=3D"internalDFN" id=3D=
"ref-for-dom-mediasource-24"><code>MediaSource</code></a>.
            </li>
            <li>Update the attribute to be <var data-type=3D"MediaSourceHan=
dle">created handle</var>.
            </li>
          </ol>
        </li>
        <li>Return the <a data-link-type=3D"idl" data-lt=3D"MediaSourceHand=
le" href=3D"https://w3c.github.io/media-source/#dom-mediasourcehandle" clas=
s=3D"internalDFN" id=3D"ref-for-dom-mediasourcehandle-4"><code>MediaSourceH=
andle</code></a> object that is this attribute's value.
        </li>
      </ol>
      </section><section id=3D"sourcebuffers-attribute"><div class=3D"heade=
r-wrapper"><h3 id=3D"x3-2-sourcebuffers-attribute"><bdi class=3D"secno">3.2=
 </bdi>
        <dfn data-export=3D"" data-dfn-type=3D"attribute" id=3D"dom-mediaso=
urce-sourcebuffers" data-idl=3D"attribute" data-title=3D"sourceBuffers" dat=
a-dfn-for=3D"MediaSource" data-type=3D"SourceBufferList" data-lt=3D"sourceB=
uffers" data-local-lt=3D"MediaSource.sourceBuffers" tabindex=3D"0" aria-has=
popup=3D"dialog"><code>sourceBuffers</code></dfn> attribute
      </h3><a class=3D"self-link" href=3D"https://w3c.github.io/media-sourc=
e/#sourcebuffers-attribute" aria-label=3D"Permalink for Section 3.2"></a></=
div>
      <p>
        Contains the list of <a data-link-type=3D"idl" data-lt=3D"SourceBuf=
fer" href=3D"https://w3c.github.io/media-source/#dom-sourcebuffer" class=3D=
"internalDFN" id=3D"ref-for-dom-sourcebuffer-16"><code>SourceBuffer</code><=
/a> objects associated with this <a data-link-type=3D"idl" data-lt=3D"Media=
Source" href=3D"https://w3c.github.io/media-source/#dom-mediasource" class=
=3D"internalDFN" id=3D"ref-for-dom-mediasource-25"><code>MediaSource</code>=
</a>. When
        <a data-link-type=3D"idl" data-lt=3D"MediaSource" href=3D"https://w=
3c.github.io/media-source/#dom-mediasource" class=3D"internalDFN" id=3D"ref=
-for-dom-mediasource-26"><code>MediaSource</code></a>'s <a data-link-type=
=3D"idl" href=3D"https://w3c.github.io/media-source/#dom-mediasource-readys=
tate" class=3D"internalDFN" id=3D"ref-for-dom-mediasource-readystate-4"><co=
de>readyState</code></a> equals "<a data-link-type=3D"idl" href=3D"https://=
w3c.github.io/media-source/#dom-readystate-closed" class=3D"internalDFN" id=
=3D"ref-for-dom-readystate-closed-2"><code>closed</code></a>" this list
        will be empty. Once <a data-link-type=3D"idl" href=3D"https://w3c.g=
ithub.io/media-source/#dom-mediasource-readystate" class=3D"internalDFN" id=
=3D"ref-for-dom-mediasource-readystate-5"><code>readyState</code></a> trans=
itions to "<a data-link-type=3D"idl" href=3D"https://w3c.github.io/media-so=
urce/#dom-readystate-open" class=3D"internalDFN" id=3D"ref-for-dom-readysta=
te-open-2"><code>open</code></a>"
        SourceBuffer objects can be added to this list by using <a data-lin=
k-type=3D"idl" data-lt=3D"addSourceBuffer()" href=3D"https://w3c.github.io/=
media-source/#dom-mediasource-addsourcebuffer" class=3D"internalDFN" id=3D"=
ref-for-dom-mediasource-addsourcebuffer-3"><code>addSourceBuffer</code></a>=
<code>()</code>.
      </p>
      </section><section id=3D"activesourcebuffers-attribute"><div class=3D=
"header-wrapper"><h3 id=3D"x3-3-activesourcebuffers-attribute"><bdi class=
=3D"secno">3.3 </bdi>
        <dfn data-export=3D"" data-dfn-type=3D"attribute" id=3D"dom-mediaso=
urce-activesourcebuffers" data-idl=3D"attribute" data-title=3D"activeSource=
Buffers" data-dfn-for=3D"MediaSource" data-type=3D"SourceBufferList" data-l=
t=3D"activeSourceBuffers" data-local-lt=3D"MediaSource.activeSourceBuffers"=
 tabindex=3D"0" aria-haspopup=3D"dialog"><code>activeSourceBuffers</code></=
dfn> attribute
      </h3><a class=3D"self-link" href=3D"https://w3c.github.io/media-sourc=
e/#activesourcebuffers-attribute" aria-label=3D"Permalink for Section 3.3">=
</a></div>
      <p>
        Contains the subset of <a data-link-type=3D"idl" href=3D"https://w3=
c.github.io/media-source/#dom-mediasource-sourcebuffers" class=3D"internalD=
FN" id=3D"ref-for-dom-mediasource-sourcebuffers-4"><code>sourceBuffers</cod=
e></a> that are providing the
        <a data-link-type=3D"attribute" href=3D"https://html.spec.whatwg.or=
g/multipage/media.html#dom-videotrack-selected"><code>selected</code></a> v=
ideo track, the <a data-link-type=3D"attribute" href=3D"https://html.spec.w=
hatwg.org/multipage/media.html#dom-audiotrack-enabled"><code>enabled</code>=
</a> audio track(s), and the
        <code><a href=3D"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/media.html#=
dom-texttrack-showing">"showing"</a></code> or <code><a href=3D"https://htm=
l.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/media.html#dom-texttrack-hidden">"hidden"</a></=
code> text
        track(s).
      </p>
      <p>
        <a data-link-type=3D"idl" data-lt=3D"SourceBuffer" href=3D"https://=
w3c.github.io/media-source/#dom-sourcebuffer" class=3D"internalDFN" id=3D"r=
ef-for-dom-sourcebuffer-17"><code>SourceBuffer</code></a> objects in this l=
ist <em class=3D"rfc2119">MUST</em> appear in the same order as they appear=
 in the
        <a data-link-type=3D"idl" href=3D"https://w3c.github.io/media-sourc=
e/#dom-mediasource-sourcebuffers" class=3D"internalDFN" id=3D"ref-for-dom-m=
ediasource-sourcebuffers-5"><code>sourceBuffers</code></a> attribute; e.g.,=
 if only sourceBuffers[0] and
        sourceBuffers[3] are in <a data-link-type=3D"idl" href=3D"https://w=
3c.github.io/media-source/#dom-mediasource-activesourcebuffers" class=3D"in=
ternalDFN" id=3D"ref-for-dom-mediasource-activesourcebuffers-3"><code>activ=
eSourceBuffers</code></a>, then activeSourceBuffers[0]
        <em class=3D"rfc2119">MUST</em> equal sourceBuffers[0] and activeSo=
urceBuffers[1] <em class=3D"rfc2119">MUST</em> equal sourceBuffers[3].
      </p>
      <div class=3D"note" role=3D"note" id=3D"issue-container-generatedID-6=
"><div role=3D"heading" class=3D"note-title marker" id=3D"h-note-6" aria-le=
vel=3D"3"><span>Note</span></div><p class=3D"">
        Section <a href=3D"https://w3c.github.io/media-source/#active-sourc=
e-buffer-changes" data-matched-text=3D"[[[#active-source-buffer-changes]]]"=
 class=3D"sec-ref"><bdi class=3D"secno">3.15.5 </bdi>
            <span>Changes to selected/enabled track state</span></a> descri=
bes how this attribute gets updated.
      </p></div>
      </section><section id=3D"readystate-attribute"><div class=3D"header-w=
rapper"><h3 id=3D"x3-4-readystate-attribute"><bdi class=3D"secno">3.4 </bdi=
>
        <dfn data-export=3D"" data-dfn-type=3D"attribute" id=3D"dom-mediaso=
urce-readystate" data-idl=3D"attribute" data-title=3D"readyState" data-dfn-=
for=3D"MediaSource" data-type=3D"ReadyState" data-lt=3D"readyState" data-lo=
cal-lt=3D"MediaSource.readyState" tabindex=3D"0" aria-haspopup=3D"dialog"><=
code>readyState</code></dfn> attribute
      </h3><a class=3D"self-link" href=3D"https://w3c.github.io/media-sourc=
e/#readystate-attribute" aria-label=3D"Permalink for Section 3.4"></a></div=
>
      <p>
        Indicates the current state of the <a href=3D"https://w3c.github.io=
/media-source/#dom-mediasource" class=3D"internalDFN" data-link-type=3D"idl=
" id=3D"ref-for-dom-mediasource-27"><code>MediaSource</code></a> object. Wh=
en the <a href=3D"https://w3c.github.io/media-source/#dom-mediasource" clas=
s=3D"internalDFN" data-link-type=3D"idl" id=3D"ref-for-dom-mediasource-28">=
<code>MediaSource</code></a>
        is created <a data-link-type=3D"idl" href=3D"https://w3c.github.io/=
media-source/#dom-mediasource-readystate" class=3D"internalDFN" id=3D"ref-f=
or-dom-mediasource-readystate-6"><code>readyState</code></a> <em class=3D"r=
fc2119">MUST</em> be set to "<a data-link-type=3D"idl" href=3D"https://w3c.=
github.io/media-source/#dom-readystate-closed" class=3D"internalDFN" id=3D"=
ref-for-dom-readystate-closed-3"><code>closed</code></a>".
      </p>
      </section><section id=3D"duration-attribute"><div class=3D"header-wra=
pper"><h3 id=3D"x3-5-duration-attribute"><bdi class=3D"secno">3.5 </bdi>
        <dfn data-export=3D"" data-dfn-type=3D"attribute" id=3D"dom-mediaso=
urce-duration" data-idl=3D"attribute" data-title=3D"duration" data-dfn-for=
=3D"MediaSource" data-type=3D"unrestricted double" data-lt=3D"duration" dat=
a-local-lt=3D"MediaSource.duration" tabindex=3D"0" aria-haspopup=3D"dialog"=
><code>duration</code></dfn> attribute
      </h3><a class=3D"self-link" href=3D"https://w3c.github.io/media-sourc=
e/#duration-attribute" aria-label=3D"Permalink for Section 3.5"></a></div>
      <p>
        Allows the web application to set the presentation duration. The du=
ration is initially set
        to NaN when the <a href=3D"https://w3c.github.io/media-source/#dom-=
mediasource" class=3D"internalDFN" data-link-type=3D"idl" id=3D"ref-for-dom=
-mediasource-29"><code>MediaSource</code></a> object is created.
      </p>
      <p>
        On getting, run the following steps:
      </p>
      <ol>
        <li>If the <a data-link-type=3D"idl" href=3D"https://w3c.github.io/=
media-source/#dom-mediasource-readystate" class=3D"internalDFN" id=3D"ref-f=
or-dom-mediasource-readystate-7"><code>readyState</code></a> attribute is "=
<a data-link-type=3D"idl" href=3D"https://w3c.github.io/media-source/#dom-r=
eadystate-closed" class=3D"internalDFN" id=3D"ref-for-dom-readystate-closed=
-4"><code>closed</code></a>" then return
        NaN and abort these steps.
        </li>
        <li>Return the current value of the attribute.
        </li>
      </ol>
      <p>
        On setting, run the following steps:
      </p>
      <ol>
        <li>If the value being set is negative or NaN then throw a <a data-=
link-type=3D"exception" data-lt=3D"TypeError" href=3D"https://webidl.spec.w=
hatwg.org/#exceptiondef-typeerror"><code>TypeError</code></a> exception and
        abort these steps.
        </li>
        <li>If the <a data-link-type=3D"idl" href=3D"https://w3c.github.io/=
media-source/#dom-mediasource-readystate" class=3D"internalDFN" id=3D"ref-f=
or-dom-mediasource-readystate-8"><code>readyState</code></a> attribute is n=
ot "<a data-link-type=3D"idl" href=3D"https://w3c.github.io/media-source/#d=
om-readystate-open" class=3D"internalDFN" id=3D"ref-for-dom-readystate-open=
-3"><code>open</code></a>" then throw
        an <a data-link-type=3D"exception" data-lt=3D"InvalidStateError" hr=
ef=3D"https://webidl.spec.whatwg.org/#invalidstateerror"><code>InvalidState=
Error</code></a> exception and abort these steps.
        </li>
        <li>If the <a data-link-type=3D"idl" href=3D"https://w3c.github.io/=
media-source/#dom-sourcebuffer-updating" class=3D"internalDFN" id=3D"ref-fo=
r-dom-sourcebuffer-updating-1"><code>updating</code></a> attribute equals t=
rue on any <a data-link-type=3D"idl" data-lt=3D"SourceBuffer" href=3D"https=
://w3c.github.io/media-source/#dom-sourcebuffer" class=3D"internalDFN" id=
=3D"ref-for-dom-sourcebuffer-18"><code>SourceBuffer</code></a> in
        <a data-link-type=3D"idl" href=3D"https://w3c.github.io/media-sourc=
e/#dom-mediasource-sourcebuffers" class=3D"internalDFN" id=3D"ref-for-dom-m=
ediasource-sourcebuffers-6"><code>sourceBuffers</code></a>, then throw an <=
a data-link-type=3D"exception" data-lt=3D"InvalidStateError" href=3D"https:=
//webidl.spec.whatwg.org/#invalidstateerror"><code>InvalidStateError</code>=
</a> exception and abort
        these steps.
        </li>
        <li>Run the <a data-link-type=3D"dfn|abstract-op" href=3D"https://w=
3c.github.io/media-source/#dfn-duration-change" class=3D"internalDFN" id=3D=
"ref-for-dfn-duration-change-1">duration change</a> algorithm with <var dat=
a-type=3D"unrestricted double">new duration</var> set to
        the value being assigned to this attribute.
          <div class=3D"note" role=3D"note" id=3D"issue-container-generated=
ID-7"><div role=3D"heading" class=3D"note-title marker" id=3D"h-note-7" ari=
a-level=3D"3"><span>Note</span></div><p class=3D"">
            The <a data-link-type=3D"dfn|abstract-op" href=3D"https://w3c.g=
ithub.io/media-source/#dfn-duration-change" class=3D"internalDFN" id=3D"ref=
-for-dfn-duration-change-2">duration change</a> algorithm will adjust <var =
data-type=3D"unrestricted double">new duration</var> higher if there is any
            currently buffered coded frame with a higher end time.
          </p></div>
          <div class=3D"note" role=3D"note" id=3D"issue-container-generated=
ID-8"><div role=3D"heading" class=3D"note-title marker" id=3D"h-note-8" ari=
a-level=3D"3"><span>Note</span></div><p class=3D"">
            <a data-link-type=3D"idl" data-lt=3D"appendBuffer()" href=3D"ht=
tps://w3c.github.io/media-source/#dom-sourcebuffer-appendbuffer" class=3D"i=
nternalDFN" id=3D"ref-for-dom-sourcebuffer-appendbuffer-1"><code>appendBuff=
er</code></a><code>()</code> and <a data-link-type=3D"idl" data-lt=3D"endOf=
Stream()" href=3D"https://w3c.github.io/media-source/#dom-mediasource-endof=
stream" class=3D"internalDFN" id=3D"ref-for-dom-mediasource-endofstream-3">=
<code>endOfStream</code></a><code>()</code> can update the
            duration under certain circumstances.
          </p></div>
        </li>
      </ol>
      </section><section id=3D"canconstructindedicatedworker-attribute"><di=
v class=3D"header-wrapper"><h3 id=3D"x3-6-canconstructindedicatedworker-att=
ribute"><bdi class=3D"secno">3.6 </bdi>
        <dfn data-export=3D"" data-dfn-type=3D"attribute" id=3D"dom-mediaso=
urce-canconstructindedicatedworker" data-idl=3D"attribute" data-title=3D"ca=
nConstructInDedicatedWorker" data-dfn-for=3D"MediaSource" data-type=3D"bool=
ean" data-lt=3D"canConstructInDedicatedWorker" data-local-lt=3D"MediaSource=
.canConstructInDedicatedWorker" tabindex=3D"0" aria-haspopup=3D"dialog"><co=
de>canConstructInDedicatedWorker</code></dfn> attribute
      </h3><a class=3D"self-link" href=3D"https://w3c.github.io/media-sourc=
e/#canconstructindedicatedworker-attribute" aria-label=3D"Permalink for Sec=
tion 3.6"></a></div>
      <p>
        Returns true.
      </p>
      <div class=3D"note" role=3D"note" id=3D"issue-container-generatedID-9=
"><div role=3D"heading" class=3D"note-title marker" id=3D"h-note-9" aria-le=
vel=3D"3"><span>Note</span></div><p class=3D"">
        This attribute enables main thread and dedicated worker feature det=
ection of support for
        creating and using a <a data-link-type=3D"idl" data-lt=3D"MediaSour=
ce" href=3D"https://w3c.github.io/media-source/#dom-mediasource" class=3D"i=
nternalDFN" id=3D"ref-for-dom-mediasource-30"><code>MediaSource</code></a> =
object in a dedicated worker, and mitigates the need
        for higher latency detection polyfills like attempting creation of =
a <a data-link-type=3D"idl" data-lt=3D"MediaSource" href=3D"https://w3c.git=
hub.io/media-source/#dom-mediasource" class=3D"internalDFN" id=3D"ref-for-d=
om-mediasource-31"><code>MediaSource</code></a> object
        from a dedicated worker, especially if the feature is not supported=
.
      </p></div>
      </section><section id=3D"addsourcebuffer-method"><div class=3D"header=
-wrapper"><h3 id=3D"x3-7-addsourcebuffer-method"><bdi class=3D"secno">3.7 <=
/bdi>
        <dfn data-export=3D"" data-dfn-type=3D"method" id=3D"dom-mediasourc=
e-addsourcebuffer" data-idl=3D"operation" data-title=3D"addSourceBuffer()" =
data-dfn-for=3D"MediaSource" data-type=3D"SourceBuffer" data-lt=3D"addSourc=
eBuffer()|addSourceBuffer(type)" data-local-lt=3D"MediaSource.addSourceBuff=
