rface" data-lt=3D"HTMLMediaElement" href=3D"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/mu=
ltipage/media.html#htmlmediaelement"><code>HTMLMediaElement</code></a>'s
        <a data-link-type=3D"attribute" href=3D"https://html.spec.whatwg.or=
g/multipage/media.html#dom-media-seekable"><code>seekable</code></a> behavi=
or.
