e" class=3D"internalDFN" id=3D"ref-for-dfn-live-seekable-range-2"><code>[[l=
ive seekable range]]</code></a> to be a new <a href=3D"https://html.spec.wh=
atwg.org/multipage/media.html#normalised-timeranges-object">normalized Time=
Ranges object</a> containing a single range whose start position is
        <var data-type=3D"double">start</var> and end position is <var data=
-type=3D"double">end</var>.
        </li>
      </ol></section><section id=3D"clearliveseekablerange-method"><div cla=
