ensions" data-matched-text=3D"[[[#htmlmediaelement-extensions]]]" class=3D"=
sec-ref"><bdi class=3D"secno">10. </bdi>
        HTMLMediaElement Extensions</a> to modify <a data-link-type=3D"inte=
rface" data-lt=3D"HTMLMediaElement" href=3D"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/mu=
