or.
      </p>
     =20
      <p>When this method is invoked, the user agent must run the following=
 steps:</p><ol class=3D"method-algorithm">
        <li>If the <a data-link-type=3D"idl" href=3D"https://w3c.github.io/=
media-source/#dom-mediasource-readystate" class=3D"internalDFN" id=3D"ref-f=
or-dom-mediasource-readystate-12"><code>readyState</code></a> attribute is =
not "<a data-link-type=3D"idl" href=3D"https://w3c.github.io/media-source/#=
dom-readystate-open" class=3D"internalDFN" id=3D"ref-for-dom-readystate-ope=
n-7"><code>open</code></a>" then throw
        an <a data-link-type=3D"exception" data-lt=3D"InvalidStateError" hr=
ef=3D"https://webidl.spec.whatwg.org/#invalidstateerror"><code>InvalidState=
