-type=3D"idl" href=3D"https://w3c.github.io/media-source/#dom-mediasource-r=
eadystate" class=3D"internalDFN" id=3D"ref-for-dom-mediasource-readystate-1=
5"><code>readyState</code></a> transitions from "<a data-link-type=3D"idl" =
