rming to this version of
            the specification may still fire these two events as these [<ci=
te><a class=3D"bibref" data-link-type=3D"biblio" href=3D"https://w3c.github=
.io/media-source/#bib-html" title=3D"HTML Standard">HTML</a></cite>] refere=
nces changed
