e=3D"dfn" href=3D"https://dom.spec.whatwg.org/#concept-event-fire">fire an =
event</a> named
            <a data-link-type=3D"event" href=3D"https://html.spec.whatwg.or=
g/multipage/media.html#event-media-emptied">emptied</a> at the media elemen=
t. These steps <em class=3D"rfc2119">SHOULD</em> be run right
