ker" class=3D"internalDFN" id=3D"ref-for-dfn-port-to-worker-5"><code>[[port=
 to worker]]</code></a> null.
                    </li>
                    <li>Set <a data-link-type=3D"attribute" data-lt=3D"[[ch=
annel with worker]]" href=3D"https://w3c.github.io/media-source/#dfn-channe=
l-with-worker" class=3D"internalDFN" id=3D"ref-for-dfn-channel-with-worker-=
