dWorkerGlobalScope</code></a> <a data-link-type=3D"idl" data-lt=3D"MediaSou=
rce" href=3D"https://w3c.github.io/media-source/#dom-mediasource" class=3D"=
internalDFN" id=3D"ref-for-dom-mediasource-81"><code>MediaSource</code></a>=
.
                    </li>
                  </ol>
                </dd>
                <dt>
                  Otherwise, the <a data-link-type=3D"idl" data-lt=3D"Media=
Source" href=3D"https://w3c.github.io/media-source/#dom-mediasource" class=
=3D"internalDFN" id=3D"ref-for-dom-mediasource-82"><code>MediaSource</code>=
</a> was constructed in a <a data-link-type=3D"interface" data-lt=3D"Window=
" href=3D"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/nav-history-apis.html#wind=
ow"><code>Window</code></a>:
