/multipage/nav-history-apis.html#window"><code>Window</code></a> <a data-li=
nk-type=3D"idl" data-lt=3D"MediaSource" href=3D"https://w3c.github.io/media=
-source/#dom-mediasource" class=3D"internalDFN" id=3D"ref-for-dom-mediasour=
ce-83"><code>MediaSource</code></a>.
                </dd>
              </dl>
            </li>
            <li>Set <a data-link-type=3D"attribute" data-lt=3D"[[port to ma=
in]]" href=3D"https://w3c.github.io/media-source/#dfn-port-to-main" class=
=3D"internalDFN" id=3D"ref-for-dfn-port-to-main-4"><code>[[port to main]]</=
code></a> null.
            </li>
            <li>Set the <a data-link-type=3D"idl" href=3D"https://w3c.githu=
b.io/media-source/#dom-mediasource-readystate" class=3D"internalDFN" id=3D"=
