ediaSource" href=3D"https://w3c.github.io/media-source/#dom-managedmediasou=
rce" class=3D"internalDFN" id=3D"ref-for-dom-managedmediasource-3"><code>Ma=
nagedMediaSource</code></a>, then set <a data-link-type=3D"idl" href=3D"htt=
ps://w3c.github.io/media-source/#dom-managedmediasource-streaming" class=3D=
"internalDFN" id=3D"ref-for-dom-managedmediasource-streaming-1"><code>strea=
