r" href=3D"https://w3c.github.io/media-source/#dfn-removesourcebuffer" clas=
s=3D"internalDFN" id=3D"ref-for-dfn-removesourcebuffer-3"><code>removesourc=
ebuffer</code></a> at
            <a data-link-type=3D"idl" href=3D"https://w3c.github.io/media-s=
ource/#dom-mediasource-activesourcebuffers" class=3D"internalDFN" id=3D"ref=
-for-dom-mediasource-activesourcebuffers-8"><code>activeSourceBuffers</code=
></a>.
            </li>
            <li>Remove all the <a data-link-type=3D"idl" data-lt=3D"SourceB=
uffer" href=3D"https://w3c.github.io/media-source/#dom-sourcebuffer" class=
=3D"internalDFN" id=3D"ref-for-dom-sourcebuffer-28"><code>SourceBuffer</cod=
