ef-for-dom-mediasource-sourcebuffers-16"><code>sourceBuffers</code></a>.
            </li>
            <li><a data-link-type=3D"dfn" href=3D"https://html.spec.whatwg.=
org/multipage/webappapis.html#queue-a-task">Queue a task</a> to <a data-lin=
k-type=3D"dfn" href=3D"https://dom.spec.whatwg.org/#concept-event-fire">fir=
