r" href=3D"https://w3c.github.io/media-source/#dfn-removesourcebuffer" clas=
s=3D"internalDFN" id=3D"ref-for-dfn-removesourcebuffer-4"><code>removesourc=
ebuffer</code></a> at
            <a data-link-type=3D"idl" href=3D"https://w3c.github.io/media-s=
ource/#dom-mediasource-sourcebuffers" class=3D"internalDFN" id=3D"ref-for-d=
om-mediasource-sourcebuffers-17"><code>sourceBuffers</code></a>.
