        <dl class=3D"attributes" data-dfn-for=3D"SourceBuffer">
          <dt>
            <dfn data-export=3D"" data-dfn-type=3D"attribute" id=3D"dom-sou=
rcebuffer-mode" data-idl=3D"attribute" data-title=3D"mode" data-dfn-for=3D"=
SourceBuffer" data-type=3D"AppendMode" data-lt=3D"mode" data-local-lt=3D"So=
urceBuffer.mode" tabindex=3D"0" aria-haspopup=3D"dialog"><code>mode</code><=
/dfn> of type <a href=3D"https://w3c.github.io/media-source/#dom-appendmode=
" class=3D"internalDFN" data-link-type=3D"idl" id=3D"ref-for-dom-appendmode=
-2"><code>AppendMode</code></a>
          </dt>
          <dd>
            <p>
              Controls how a sequence of <a data-link-type=3D"dfn|abstract-=
op" href=3D"https://w3c.github.io/media-source/#dfn-media-segment" class=3D=
"internalDFN" id=3D"ref-for-dfn-media-segment-5">media segments</a> are han=
dled. This attribute is
              initially set by <a data-link-type=3D"idl" data-lt=3D"addSour=
ceBuffer()" href=3D"https://w3c.github.io/media-source/#dom-mediasource-add=
sourcebuffer" class=3D"internalDFN" id=3D"ref-for-dom-mediasource-addsource=
buffer-5"><code>addSourceBuffer</code></a><code>()</code> after the object =
is created, and
              can be updated by <a data-link-type=3D"idl" data-lt=3D"change=
Type()" href=3D"https://w3c.github.io/media-source/#dom-sourcebuffer-change=
type" class=3D"internalDFN" id=3D"ref-for-dom-sourcebuffer-changetype-4"><c=
ode>changeType</code></a><code>()</code> or setting this attribute.
            </p>
            <p>
              On getting, Return the initial value or the last value that w=
as successfully set.
            </p>
            <p>
              On setting, run the following steps:
            </p>
            <ol>
              <li>If this object has been removed from the <a data-link-typ=
e=3D"idl" href=3D"https://w3c.github.io/media-source/#dom-mediasource-sourc=
ebuffers" class=3D"internalDFN" id=3D"ref-for-dom-mediasource-sourcebuffers=
-21"><code>sourceBuffers</code></a> attribute
              of the <a data-link-type=3D"dfn|abstract-op" href=3D"https://=
w3c.github.io/media-source/#parent-media-source" class=3D"internalDFN" id=
=3D"ref-for-parent-media-source-1">parent media source</a>, then throw an <=
a data-link-type=3D"exception" data-lt=3D"InvalidStateError" href=3D"https:=
//webidl.spec.whatwg.org/#invalidstateerror"><code>InvalidStateError</code>=
</a> exception and
              abort these steps.
              </li>
              <li>If the <a data-link-type=3D"idl" href=3D"https://w3c.gith=
ub.io/media-source/#dom-sourcebuffer-updating" class=3D"internalDFN" id=3D"=
ref-for-dom-sourcebuffer-updating-6"><code>updating</code></a> attribute eq=
uals true, then throw an
              <a data-link-type=3D"exception" data-lt=3D"InvalidStateError"=
 href=3D"https://webidl.spec.whatwg.org/#invalidstateerror"><code>InvalidSt=
ateError</code></a> exception and abort these steps.
