       =20
        <dl class=3D"methods" data-dfn-for=3D"SourceBuffer">
          <dt>
            <dfn id=3D"dom-sourcebuffer-appendbuffer" data-export=3D"" data=
-dfn-type=3D"method" data-idl=3D"operation" data-title=3D"appendBuffer" dat=
a-dfn-for=3D"SourceBuffer" data-type=3D"undefined" data-lt=3D"appendBuffer(=
)|appendBuffer(data)" data-local-lt=3D"SourceBuffer.appendBuffer|SourceBuff=
er.appendBuffer()|appendBuffer" tabindex=3D"0" aria-haspopup=3D"dialog"><co=
de>appendBuffer</code></dfn>
          </dt>
          <dd>
            <p>
              Appends the segment data in an <code><a href=3D"https://www.w=
3.org/TR/WebIDL-1/#common-BufferSource" class=3D"idlType">BufferSource</a><=
/code>[<cite><a class=3D"bibref" data-link-type=3D"biblio" href=3D"https://=
w3c.github.io/media-source/#bib-webidl" title=3D"Web IDL Standard">WEBIDL</=
a></cite>] to
              the <a data-link-type=3D"idl" data-lt=3D"SourceBuffer" href=
=3D"https://w3c.github.io/media-source/#dom-sourcebuffer" class=3D"internal=
DFN" id=3D"ref-for-dom-sourcebuffer-51"><code>SourceBuffer</code></a>.
            </p>
           =20
          <p>When this method is invoked, the user agent must run the follo=
wing steps:</p><ol class=3D"method-algorithm">
              <li>Run the <a data-link-type=3D"dfn|abstract-op" href=3D"htt=
ps://w3c.github.io/media-source/#dfn-prepare-append" class=3D"internalDFN" =
id=3D"ref-for-dfn-prepare-append-1">prepare append</a> algorithm.
              </li>
              <li>Add <var data-type=3D"BufferSource">data</var> to the end=
 of the <a data-link-type=3D"attribute" data-lt=3D"[[input buffer]]" href=
=3D"https://w3c.github.io/media-source/#dfn-input-buffer" class=3D"internal=
DFN" id=3D"ref-for-dfn-input-buffer-1"><code>[[input buffer]]</code></a>.
              </li>
              <li>Set the <a data-link-type=3D"idl" href=3D"https://w3c.git=
hub.io/media-source/#dom-sourcebuffer-updating" class=3D"internalDFN" id=3D=
"ref-for-dom-sourcebuffer-updating-10"><code>updating</code></a> attribute =
to true.
              </li>
              <li><a data-link-type=3D"dfn" href=3D"https://html.spec.whatw=
g.org/multipage/webappapis.html#queue-a-task">Queue a task</a> to <a data-l=
ink-type=3D"dfn" href=3D"https://dom.spec.whatwg.org/#concept-event-fire">f=
ire an event</a> named <a data-link-type=3D"idl" data-lt=3D"updatestart" hr=
ef=3D"https://w3c.github.io/media-source/#dfn-updatestart" class=3D"interna=
lDFN" id=3D"ref-for-dfn-updatestart-2"><code>updatestart</code></a> at this
              <a data-link-type=3D"idl" data-lt=3D"SourceBuffer" href=3D"ht=
tps://w3c.github.io/media-source/#dom-sourcebuffer" class=3D"internalDFN" i=
d=3D"ref-for-dom-sourcebuffer-52"><code>SourceBuffer</code></a> object.
              </li>
              <li>Asynchronously run the <a data-link-type=3D"dfn|abstract-=
op" href=3D"https://w3c.github.io/media-source/#dfn-buffer-append" class=3D=
"internalDFN" id=3D"ref-for-dfn-buffer-append-2">buffer append</a> algorith=
m.
              </li>
            </ol></dd>
          <dt>
            <dfn data-export=3D"" data-dfn-type=3D"method" id=3D"dom-source=
buffer-abort" data-idl=3D"operation" data-title=3D"abort" data-dfn-for=3D"S=
ourceBuffer" data-type=3D"undefined" data-lt=3D"abort()" data-local-lt=3D"S=
ourceBuffer.abort|SourceBuffer.abort()|abort" tabindex=3D"0" aria-haspopup=
=3D"dialog"><code>abort</code></dfn>
          </dt>
          <dd>
            <p>
              Aborts the current segment and resets the segment parser.
            </p>
           =20
          <p>When this method is invoked, the user agent must run the follo=
wing steps:</p><ol class=3D"method-algorithm">
              <li>If this object has been removed from the <a data-link-typ=
e=3D"idl" href=3D"https://w3c.github.io/media-source/#dom-mediasource-sourc=
ebuffers" class=3D"internalDFN" id=3D"ref-for-dom-mediasource-sourcebuffers=
-26"><code>sourceBuffers</code></a> attribute
              of the <a data-link-type=3D"dfn|abstract-op" href=3D"https://=
w3c.github.io/media-source/#parent-media-source" class=3D"internalDFN" id=
=3D"ref-for-parent-media-source-12">parent media source</a> then throw an <=
a data-link-type=3D"exception" data-lt=3D"InvalidStateError" href=3D"https:=
//webidl.spec.whatwg.org/#invalidstateerror"><code>InvalidStateError</code>=
</a> exception and
              abort these steps.
              </li>
              <li>If the <a data-link-type=3D"idl" href=3D"https://w3c.gith=
ub.io/media-source/#dom-mediasource-readystate" class=3D"internalDFN" id=3D=
"ref-for-dom-mediasource-readystate-28"><code>readyState</code></a> attribu=
te of the <a data-link-type=3D"dfn|abstract-op" href=3D"https://w3c.github.=
io/media-source/#parent-media-source" class=3D"internalDFN" id=3D"ref-for-p=
arent-media-source-13">parent media source</a> is not
              in the "<a data-link-type=3D"idl" href=3D"https://w3c.github.=
io/media-source/#dom-readystate-open" class=3D"internalDFN" id=3D"ref-for-d=
om-readystate-open-16"><code>open</code></a>" state then throw an <a data-l=
ink-type=3D"exception" data-lt=3D"InvalidStateError" href=3D"https://webidl=
.spec.whatwg.org/#invalidstateerror"><code>InvalidStateError</code></a> exc=
eption
              and abort these steps.
              </li>
              <li>If the <a data-link-type=3D"dfn|abstract-op" href=3D"http=
s://w3c.github.io/media-source/#dfn-range-removal" class=3D"internalDFN" id=
=3D"ref-for-dfn-range-removal-1">range removal</a> algorithm is running, th=
en throw an
              <a data-link-type=3D"exception" data-lt=3D"InvalidStateError"=
 href=3D"https://webidl.spec.whatwg.org/#invalidstateerror"><code>InvalidSt=
ateError</code></a> exception and abort these steps.
              </li>
              <li>If the <a data-link-type=3D"idl" href=3D"https://w3c.gith=
ub.io/media-source/#dom-sourcebuffer-updating" class=3D"internalDFN" id=3D"=
ref-for-dom-sourcebuffer-updating-11"><code>updating</code></a> attribute e=
quals true, then run the following
              steps:
                <ol>
                  <li>Abort the <a data-link-type=3D"dfn|abstract-op" href=
=3D"https://w3c.github.io/media-source/#dfn-buffer-append" class=3D"interna=
lDFN" id=3D"ref-for-dfn-buffer-append-3">buffer append</a> algorithm if it =
is running.
                  </li>
                  <li>Set the <a data-link-type=3D"idl" href=3D"https://w3c=
.github.io/media-source/#dom-sourcebuffer-updating" class=3D"internalDFN" i=
d=3D"ref-for-dom-sourcebuffer-updating-12"><code>updating</code></a> attrib=
ute to false.
                  </li>
                  <li><a data-link-type=3D"dfn" href=3D"https://html.spec.w=
hatwg.org/multipage/webappapis.html#queue-a-task">Queue a task</a> to <a da=
ta-link-type=3D"dfn" href=3D"https://dom.spec.whatwg.org/#concept-event-fir=
e">fire an event</a> named <a data-link-type=3D"idl" data-lt=3D"abort" href=
=3D"https://w3c.github.io/media-source/#dfn-abort" class=3D"internalDFN" id=
=3D"ref-for-dfn-abort-3"><code>abort</code></a> at this
                  <a data-link-type=3D"idl" data-lt=3D"SourceBuffer" href=
=3D"https://w3c.github.io/media-source/#dom-sourcebuffer" class=3D"internal=
DFN" id=3D"ref-for-dom-sourcebuffer-53"><code>SourceBuffer</code></a> objec=
t.
                  </li>
                  <li><a data-link-type=3D"dfn" href=3D"https://html.spec.w=
hatwg.org/multipage/webappapis.html#queue-a-task">Queue a task</a> to <a da=
ta-link-type=3D"dfn" href=3D"https://dom.spec.whatwg.org/#concept-event-fir=
