hatwg.org/multipage/webappapis.html#queue-a-task">Queue a task</a> to <a da=
ta-link-type=3D"dfn" href=3D"https://dom.spec.whatwg.org/#concept-event-fir=
e">fire an event</a> named <a data-link-type=3D"idl" data-lt=3D"sourceopen"=
 href=3D"https://w3c.github.io/media-source/#dfn-sourceopen" class=3D"inter=
nalDFN" id=3D"ref-for-dfn-sourceopen-5"><code>sourceopen</code></a> at the =
<a data-link-type=3D"dfn|abstract-op" href=3D"https://w3c.github.io/media-s=
ource/#parent-media-source" class=3D"internalDFN" id=3D"ref-for-parent-medi=
