o/media-source/#dom-mediasource-duration" class=3D"internalDFN" id=3D"ref-f=
or-dom-mediasource-duration-7"><code>duration</code></a> equals NaN, then t=
hrow a <a data-link-type=3D"exception" data-lt=3D"TypeError" href=3D"https:=
//webidl.spec.whatwg.org/#exceptiondef-typeerror"><code>TypeError</code></a=
> exception and
              abort these steps.
              </li>
              <li>If <var data-type=3D"double">start</var> is negative or g=
reater than <a data-link-type=3D"idl" href=3D"https://w3c.github.io/media-s=
ource/#dom-mediasource-duration" class=3D"internalDFN" id=3D"ref-for-dom-me=
diasource-duration-8"><code>duration</code></a>, then
              throw a <a data-link-type=3D"exception" data-lt=3D"TypeError"=
 href=3D"https://webidl.spec.whatwg.org/#exceptiondef-typeerror"><code>Type=
Error</code></a> exception and abort these steps.
