ub.io/media-source/#dom-mediasource-readystate" class=3D"internalDFN" id=3D=
"ref-for-dom-mediasource-readystate-31"><code>readyState</code></a> attribu=
te of the <a data-link-type=3D"dfn|abstract-op" href=3D"https://w3c.github.=
io/media-source/#parent-media-source" class=3D"internalDFN" id=3D"ref-for-p=
arent-media-source-20">parent media source</a> is in
