                <ol>
                  <li>Set the <a data-link-type=3D"idl" href=3D"https://w3c=
.github.io/media-source/#dom-mediasource-readystate" class=3D"internalDFN" =
id=3D"ref-for-dom-mediasource-readystate-32"><code>readyState</code></a> at=
tribute of the <a data-link-type=3D"dfn|abstract-op" href=3D"https://w3c.gi=
thub.io/media-source/#parent-media-source" class=3D"internalDFN" id=3D"ref-=
for-parent-media-source-21">parent media source</a>
