      <section id=3D"track-buffers"><div class=3D"header-wrapper"><h3 id=3D=
"x5-3-track-buffers"><bdi class=3D"secno">5.3 </bdi>
          Track Buffers
        </h3><a class=3D"self-link" href=3D"https://w3c.github.io/media-sou=
rce/#track-buffers" aria-label=3D"Permalink for Section 5.3"></a></div>
       =20
        <p>
          A <dfn id=3D"track-buffer" data-plurals=3D"track buffers" tabinde=
x=3D"0" aria-haspopup=3D"dialog" data-dfn-type=3D"dfn">track buffer</dfn> s=
tores the <a data-link-type=3D"dfn|abstract-op" href=3D"https://w3c.github.=
io/media-source/#dfn-track-description" class=3D"internalDFN" id=3D"ref-for=
-dfn-track-description-2">track descriptions</a> and <a data-link-type=3D"d=
fn|abstract-op" href=3D"https://w3c.github.io/media-source/#dfn-coded-frame=
" class=3D"internalDFN" id=3D"ref-for-dfn-coded-frame-13">coded frames</a> =
for an individual track. The track buffer is updated as <a data-link-type=
=3D"dfn|abstract-op" href=3D"https://w3c.github.io/media-source/#dfn-initia=
lization-segment" class=3D"internalDFN" id=3D"ref-for-dfn-initialization-se=
gment-5">initialization segments</a> and <a data-link-type=3D"dfn|abstract-=
op" href=3D"https://w3c.github.io/media-source/#dfn-media-segment" class=3D=
"internalDFN" id=3D"ref-for-dfn-media-segment-7">media segments</a> are app=
ended to the <a data-link-type=3D"idl" data-lt=3D"SourceBuffer" href=3D"htt=
ps://w3c.github.io/media-source/#dom-sourcebuffer" class=3D"internalDFN" id=
=3D"ref-for-dom-sourcebuffer-60"><code>SourceBuffer</code></a>.
        </p>
        <p>
          Each <a data-link-type=3D"dfn|abstract-op" href=3D"https://w3c.gi=
thub.io/media-source/#track-buffer" class=3D"internalDFN" id=3D"ref-for-tra=
ck-buffer-8">track buffer</a> has a <dfn id=3D"last-decode-timestamp" tabin=
dex=3D"0" aria-haspopup=3D"dialog" data-dfn-type=3D"dfn">last decode timest=
amp</dfn>
          variable that stores the decode timestamp of the last <a data-lin=
k-type=3D"dfn|abstract-op" href=3D"https://w3c.github.io/media-source/#dfn-=
coded-frame" class=3D"internalDFN" id=3D"ref-for-dfn-coded-frame-14">coded =
frame</a> appended in the
          current <a data-link-type=3D"dfn|abstract-op" href=3D"https://w3c=
.github.io/media-source/#dfn-coded-frame-group" class=3D"internalDFN" id=3D=
"ref-for-dfn-coded-frame-group-1">coded frame group</a>. The variable is in=
itially unset to indicate that no
          <a data-link-type=3D"dfn|abstract-op" href=3D"https://w3c.github.=
io/media-source/#dfn-coded-frame" class=3D"internalDFN" id=3D"ref-for-dfn-c=
oded-frame-15">coded frames</a> have been appended yet.
        </p>
        <p>
          Each <a data-link-type=3D"dfn|abstract-op" href=3D"https://w3c.gi=
thub.io/media-source/#track-buffer" class=3D"internalDFN" id=3D"ref-for-tra=
ck-buffer-9">track buffer</a> has a <dfn id=3D"last-frame-duration" tabinde=
x=3D"0" aria-haspopup=3D"dialog" data-dfn-type=3D"dfn">last frame duration<=
/dfn>
          variable that stores the <a data-link-type=3D"dfn|abstract-op" hr=
ef=3D"https://w3c.github.io/media-source/#dfn-coded-frame-duration" class=
=3D"internalDFN" id=3D"ref-for-dfn-coded-frame-duration-5">coded frame dura=
tion</a> of the last <a data-link-type=3D"dfn|abstract-op" href=3D"https://=
w3c.github.io/media-source/#dfn-coded-frame" class=3D"internalDFN" id=3D"re=
f-for-dfn-coded-frame-16">coded frame</a> appended in
          the current <a data-link-type=3D"dfn|abstract-op" href=3D"https:/=
/w3c.github.io/media-source/#dfn-coded-frame-group" class=3D"internalDFN" i=
d=3D"ref-for-dfn-coded-frame-group-2">coded frame group</a>. The variable i=
s initially unset to indicate that no
          <a data-link-type=3D"dfn|abstract-op" href=3D"https://w3c.github.=
io/media-source/#dfn-coded-frame" class=3D"internalDFN" id=3D"ref-for-dfn-c=
oded-frame-17">coded frames</a> have been appended yet.
