        <p>
          Each <a data-link-type=3D"dfn|abstract-op" href=3D"https://w3c.gi=
thub.io/media-source/#track-buffer" class=3D"internalDFN" id=3D"ref-for-tra=
ck-buffer-10">track buffer</a> has a <dfn id=3D"highest-end-timestamp" tabi=
ndex=3D"0" aria-haspopup=3D"dialog" data-dfn-type=3D"dfn">highest end times=
tamp</dfn>
          variable that stores the highest <a data-link-type=3D"dfn|abstrac=
t-op" href=3D"https://w3c.github.io/media-source/#dfn-coded-frame-end-times=
tamp" class=3D"internalDFN" id=3D"ref-for-dfn-coded-frame-end-timestamp-1">=
coded frame end timestamp</a> across all <a data-link-type=3D"dfn|abstract-=
op" href=3D"https://w3c.github.io/media-source/#dfn-coded-frame" class=3D"i=
nternalDFN" id=3D"ref-for-dfn-coded-frame-18">coded frames</a> in the curre=
nt <a data-link-type=3D"dfn|abstract-op" href=3D"https://w3c.github.io/medi=
a-source/#dfn-coded-frame-group" class=3D"internalDFN" id=3D"ref-for-dfn-co=
ded-frame-group-3">coded frame group</a> that were appended to this track b=
uffer.
