                </li>
                <li>Jump to the <i>loop top</i> step above.
                </li>
              </ol>
            </li>
            <li>
              <i>Need more data:</i> Return control to the calling algorith=
m.
            </li>
          </ol>
        </section>
        <section id=3D"sourcebuffer-reset-parser-state"><div class=3D"heade=
r-wrapper"><h4 id=3D"x5-5-2-reset-parser-state"><bdi class=3D"secno">5.5.2 =
</bdi>
            <dfn id=3D"dfn-reset-parser-state" tabindex=3D"0" aria-haspopup=
=3D"dialog" data-dfn-type=3D"dfn">Reset Parser State</dfn>
          </h4><a class=3D"self-link" href=3D"https://w3c.github.io/media-s=
ource/#sourcebuffer-reset-parser-state" aria-label=3D"Permalink for Section=
 5.5.2"></a></div>
         =20
          <p>
            When the parser state needs to be reset, run the following step=
s:
          </p>
          <ol>
            <li>If the <a data-link-type=3D"attribute" data-lt=3D"[[append =
state]]" href=3D"https://w3c.github.io/media-source/#dfn-append-state" clas=
s=3D"internalDFN" id=3D"ref-for-dfn-append-state-10"><code>[[append state]]=
</code></a> equals <a data-link-type=3D"dfn|abstract-op" href=3D"https://w3=
c.github.io/media-source/#sourcebuffer-parsing-media-segment" class=3D"inte=
rnalDFN" id=3D"ref-for-sourcebuffer-parsing-media-segment-5">PARSING_MEDIA_=
SEGMENT</a> and the
            <a data-link-type=3D"attribute" data-lt=3D"[[input buffer]]" hr=
ef=3D"https://w3c.github.io/media-source/#dfn-input-buffer" class=3D"intern=
alDFN" id=3D"ref-for-dfn-input-buffer-12"><code>[[input buffer]]</code></a>=
 contains some complete <a data-link-type=3D"dfn|abstract-op" href=3D"https=
://w3c.github.io/media-source/#dfn-coded-frame" class=3D"internalDFN" id=3D=
"ref-for-dfn-coded-frame-26">coded frames</a>, then run the
            <a data-link-type=3D"dfn|abstract-op" href=3D"https://w3c.githu=
b.io/media-source/#dfn-coded-frame-processing" class=3D"internalDFN" id=3D"=
ref-for-dfn-coded-frame-processing-10">coded frame processing</a> algorithm=
 until all of these complete <a data-link-type=3D"dfn|abstract-op" href=3D"=
https://w3c.github.io/media-source/#dfn-coded-frame" class=3D"internalDFN" =
id=3D"ref-for-dfn-coded-frame-27">coded frames</a> have
            been processed.
            </li>
            <li>Unset the <a data-link-type=3D"dfn|abstract-op" href=3D"htt=
ps://w3c.github.io/media-source/#last-decode-timestamp" class=3D"internalDF=
N" id=3D"ref-for-last-decode-timestamp-1">last decode timestamp</a> on all =
<a data-link-type=3D"dfn|abstract-op" href=3D"https://w3c.github.io/media-s=
ource/#track-buffer" class=3D"internalDFN" id=3D"ref-for-track-buffer-17">t=
rack buffers</a>.
            </li>
            <li>Unset the <a data-link-type=3D"dfn|abstract-op" href=3D"htt=
ps://w3c.github.io/media-source/#last-frame-duration" class=3D"internalDFN"=
 id=3D"ref-for-last-frame-duration-1">last frame duration</a> on all <a dat=
a-link-type=3D"dfn|abstract-op" href=3D"https://w3c.github.io/media-source/=
#track-buffer" class=3D"internalDFN" id=3D"ref-for-track-buffer-18">track b=
uffers</a>.
            </li>
            <li>Unset the <a data-link-type=3D"dfn|abstract-op" href=3D"htt=
ps://w3c.github.io/media-source/#highest-end-timestamp" class=3D"internalDF=
N" id=3D"ref-for-highest-end-timestamp-1">highest end timestamp</a> on all =
<a data-link-type=3D"dfn|abstract-op" href=3D"https://w3c.github.io/media-s=
ource/#track-buffer" class=3D"internalDFN" id=3D"ref-for-track-buffer-19">t=
rack buffers</a>.
            </li>
            <li>Set the <a data-link-type=3D"dfn|abstract-op" href=3D"https=
://w3c.github.io/media-source/#need-RAP-flag" class=3D"internalDFN" id=3D"r=
ef-for-need-RAP-flag-1">need random access point flag</a> on all <a data-li=
nk-type=3D"dfn|abstract-op" href=3D"https://w3c.github.io/media-source/#tra=
ck-buffer" class=3D"internalDFN" id=3D"ref-for-track-buffer-20">track buffe=
rs</a> to true.
            </li>
            <li>If the <a data-link-type=3D"idl" href=3D"https://w3c.github=
.io/media-source/#dom-sourcebuffer-mode" class=3D"internalDFN" id=3D"ref-fo=
r-dom-sourcebuffer-mode-10"><code>mode</code></a> attribute equals "<a data=
-link-type=3D"idl" href=3D"https://w3c.github.io/media-source/#dom-appendmo=
de-sequence" class=3D"internalDFN" id=3D"ref-for-dom-appendmode-sequence-9"=
><code>sequence</code></a>", then set
            the <a data-link-type=3D"attribute" data-lt=3D"[[group start ti=
mestamp]]" href=3D"https://w3c.github.io/media-source/#dfn-group-start-time=
stamp" class=3D"internalDFN" id=3D"ref-for-dfn-group-start-timestamp-3"><co=
de>[[group start timestamp]]</code></a> to the <a data-link-type=3D"attribu=
te" data-lt=3D"[[group end timestamp]]" href=3D"https://w3c.github.io/media=
-source/#dfn-group-end-timestamp" class=3D"internalDFN" id=3D"ref-for-dfn-g=
roup-end-timestamp-3"><code>[[group end timestamp]]</code></a>
            </li>
            <li>Remove all bytes from the <a data-link-type=3D"attribute" d=
ata-lt=3D"[[input buffer]]" href=3D"https://w3c.github.io/media-source/#dfn=
-input-buffer" class=3D"internalDFN" id=3D"ref-for-dfn-input-buffer-13"><co=
de>[[input buffer]]</code></a>.
            </li>
            <li>Set <a data-link-type=3D"attribute" data-lt=3D"[[append sta=
te]]" href=3D"https://w3c.github.io/media-source/#dfn-append-state" class=
=3D"internalDFN" id=3D"ref-for-dfn-append-state-11"><code>[[append state]]<=
/code></a> to <a data-link-type=3D"dfn|abstract-op" href=3D"https://w3c.git=
hub.io/media-source/#sourcebuffer-waiting-for-segment" class=3D"internalDFN=
" id=3D"ref-for-sourcebuffer-waiting-for-segment-5">WAITING_FOR_SEGMENT</a>=
.
            </li>
          </ol>
        </section>
        <section id=3D"sourcebuffer-append-error"><div class=3D"header-wrap=
per"><h4 id=3D"x5-5-3-append-error"><bdi class=3D"secno">5.5.3 </bdi>
            <dfn data-export=3D"" id=3D"dfn-append-error" tabindex=3D"0" ar=
ia-haspopup=3D"dialog" data-dfn-type=3D"dfn">Append Error</dfn>
          </h4><a class=3D"self-link" href=3D"https://w3c.github.io/media-s=
ource/#sourcebuffer-append-error" aria-label=3D"Permalink for Section 5.5.3=
"></a></div>
         =20
          <p>
            This algorithm is called when an error occurs during an append.
          </p>
          <ol>
            <li>Run the <a data-link-type=3D"dfn|abstract-op" href=3D"https=
://w3c.github.io/media-source/#dfn-reset-parser-state" class=3D"internalDFN=
" id=3D"ref-for-dfn-reset-parser-state-3">reset parser state</a> algorithm.
            </li>
            <li>Set the <a data-link-type=3D"idl" href=3D"https://w3c.githu=
b.io/media-source/#dom-sourcebuffer-updating" class=3D"internalDFN" id=3D"r=
ef-for-dom-sourcebuffer-updating-19"><code>updating</code></a> attribute to=
 false.
            </li>
            <li><a data-link-type=3D"dfn" href=3D"https://html.spec.whatwg.=
org/multipage/webappapis.html#queue-a-task">Queue a task</a> to <a data-lin=
k-type=3D"dfn" href=3D"https://dom.spec.whatwg.org/#concept-event-fire">fir=
e an event</a> named <a data-link-type=3D"idl" data-lt=3D"error" href=3D"ht=
tps://w3c.github.io/media-source/#dfn-error" class=3D"internalDFN" id=3D"re=
f-for-dfn-error-2"><code>error</code></a> at this <a data-link-type=3D"idl"=
 data-lt=3D"SourceBuffer" href=3D"https://w3c.github.io/media-source/#dom-s=
ourcebuffer" class=3D"internalDFN" id=3D"ref-for-dom-sourcebuffer-80"><code=
>SourceBuffer</code></a>
            object.
            </li>
            <li><a data-link-type=3D"dfn" href=3D"https://html.spec.whatwg.=
org/multipage/webappapis.html#queue-a-task">Queue a task</a> to <a data-lin=
k-type=3D"dfn" href=3D"https://dom.spec.whatwg.org/#concept-event-fire">fir=
e an event</a> named <a data-link-type=3D"idl" data-lt=3D"updateend" href=
=3D"https://w3c.github.io/media-source/#dfn-updateend" class=3D"internalDFN=
" id=3D"ref-for-dfn-updateend-4"><code>updateend</code></a> at this <a data=
-link-type=3D"idl" data-lt=3D"SourceBuffer" href=3D"https://w3c.github.io/m=
edia-source/#dom-sourcebuffer" class=3D"internalDFN" id=3D"ref-for-dom-sour=
cebuffer-81"><code>SourceBuffer</code></a>
            object.
            </li>
            <li>Run the <a data-link-type=3D"dfn|abstract-op" href=3D"https=
://w3c.github.io/media-source/#dfn-end-of-stream" class=3D"internalDFN" id=
=3D"ref-for-dfn-end-of-stream-2">end of stream</a> algorithm with the <var =
data-type=3D"EndOfStreamError">error</var> parameter set
            to "<a data-link-type=3D"idl" href=3D"https://w3c.github.io/med=
ia-source/#dom-endofstreamerror-decode" class=3D"internalDFN" id=3D"ref-for=
-dom-endofstreamerror-decode-3"><code>decode</code></a>".
            </li>
          </ol>
        </section>
        <section id=3D"sourcebuffer-prepare-append"><div class=3D"header-wr=
apper"><h4 id=3D"x5-5-4-prepare-append"><bdi class=3D"secno">5.5.4 </bdi>
            <dfn id=3D"dfn-prepare-append" tabindex=3D"0" aria-haspopup=3D"=
dialog" data-dfn-type=3D"dfn">Prepare Append</dfn>
          </h4><a class=3D"self-link" href=3D"https://w3c.github.io/media-s=
ource/#sourcebuffer-prepare-append" aria-label=3D"Permalink for Section 5.5=
.4"></a></div>
         =20
          <p>
            When an append operation begins, the following steps are run to=
 validate and prepare
            the <a data-link-type=3D"idl" data-lt=3D"SourceBuffer" href=3D"=
https://w3c.github.io/media-source/#dom-sourcebuffer" class=3D"internalDFN"=
 id=3D"ref-for-dom-sourcebuffer-82"><code>SourceBuffer</code></a>.
          </p>
          <ol>
            <li>If the <a data-link-type=3D"idl" data-lt=3D"SourceBuffer" h=
ref=3D"https://w3c.github.io/media-source/#dom-sourcebuffer" class=3D"inter=
nalDFN" id=3D"ref-for-dom-sourcebuffer-83"><code>SourceBuffer</code></a> ha=
s been removed from the <a data-link-type=3D"idl" href=3D"https://w3c.githu=
b.io/media-source/#dom-mediasource-sourcebuffers" class=3D"internalDFN" id=
=3D"ref-for-dom-mediasource-sourcebuffers-30"><code>sourceBuffers</code></a=
>
            attribute of the <a data-link-type=3D"dfn|abstract-op" href=3D"=
https://w3c.github.io/media-source/#parent-media-source" class=3D"internalD=
FN" id=3D"ref-for-parent-media-source-23">parent media source</a> then thro=
w an <a data-link-type=3D"exception" data-lt=3D"InvalidStateError" href=3D"=
https://webidl.spec.whatwg.org/#invalidstateerror"><code>InvalidStateError<=
/code></a> exception
            and abort these steps.
            </li>
            <li>If the <a data-link-type=3D"idl" href=3D"https://w3c.github=
.io/media-source/#dom-sourcebuffer-updating" class=3D"internalDFN" id=3D"re=
f-for-dom-sourcebuffer-updating-20"><code>updating</code></a> attribute equ=
als true, then throw an
            <a data-link-type=3D"exception" data-lt=3D"InvalidStateError" h=
ref=3D"https://webidl.spec.whatwg.org/#invalidstateerror"><code>InvalidStat=
eError</code></a> exception and abort these steps.
            </li>
            <li>Let <var data-type=3D"boolean">recent element error</var> b=
e determined as follows:
              <dl class=3D"switch">
                <dt>
                  If the <a data-link-type=3D"idl" data-lt=3D"MediaSource" =
href=3D"https://w3c.github.io/media-source/#dom-mediasource" class=3D"inter=
nalDFN" id=3D"ref-for-dom-mediasource-98"><code>MediaSource</code></a> was =
constructed in a <a data-link-type=3D"interface" data-lt=3D"Window" href=3D=
"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/nav-history-apis.html#window"><code=
>Window</code></a>
                </dt>
                <dd>
                  Let <var data-type=3D"boolean">recent element error</var>=
 be true if the <a data-link-type=3D"interface" data-lt=3D"HTMLMediaElement=
" href=3D"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/media.html#htmlmediaelemen=
t"><code>HTMLMediaElement</code></a>'s
                  <a data-link-type=3D"idl" href=3D"https://w3c.github.io/m=
edia-source/#dfn-error" class=3D"internalDFN" id=3D"ref-for-dfn-error-3"><c=
ode>error</code></a> attribute is not null. If that attribute is null, then
                  let <var data-type=3D"boolean">recent element error</var>=
 be false.
                </dd>
                <dt>
                  Otherwise
                </dt>
                <dd>
                  Let <var data-type=3D"boolean">recent element error</var>=
 be the value resulting from the steps for the
                  <a data-link-type=3D"interface" data-lt=3D"Window" href=
=3D"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/nav-history-apis.html#window"><c=
ode>Window</code></a> case, but run on the <a data-link-type=3D"interface" =
data-lt=3D"Window" href=3D"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/nav-histo=
ry-apis.html#window"><code>Window</code></a> <a data-link-type=3D"interface=
" data-lt=3D"HTMLMediaElement" href=3D"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipa=
ge/media.html#htmlmediaelement"><code>HTMLMediaElement</code></a> on any ch=
ange to
                  its <a data-link-type=3D"idl" href=3D"https://w3c.github.=
io/media-source/#dfn-error" class=3D"internalDFN" id=3D"ref-for-dfn-error-4=
"><code>error</code></a> attribute and communicated by using
                  <a data-link-type=3D"attribute" data-lt=3D"[[port to work=
er]]" href=3D"https://w3c.github.io/media-source/#dfn-port-to-worker" class=
=3D"internalDFN" id=3D"ref-for-dfn-port-to-worker-7"><code>[[port to worker=
]]</code></a> implicit messages. If such a message has
                  not yet been received, then let <var data-type=3D"boolean=
">recent element error</var> be false.
                </dd>
              </dl>
            </li>
            <li>If <var data-type=3D"boolean">recent element error</var> is=
 true, then throw an <a data-link-type=3D"exception" data-lt=3D"InvalidStat=
eError" href=3D"https://webidl.spec.whatwg.org/#invalidstateerror"><code>In=
validStateError</code></a> exception
            and abort these steps.
            </li>
            <li>
              <p>
                If the <a data-link-type=3D"idl" href=3D"https://w3c.github=
.io/media-source/#dom-mediasource-readystate" class=3D"internalDFN" id=3D"r=
ef-for-dom-mediasource-readystate-33"><code>readyState</code></a> attribute=
 of the <a data-link-type=3D"dfn|abstract-op" href=3D"https://w3c.github.io=
/media-source/#parent-media-source" class=3D"internalDFN" id=3D"ref-for-par=
ent-media-source-24">parent media source</a> is in
                the "<a data-link-type=3D"idl" href=3D"https://w3c.github.i=
o/media-source/#dom-readystate-ended" class=3D"internalDFN" id=3D"ref-for-d=
om-readystate-ended-13"><code>ended</code></a>" state then run the followin=
g steps:
              </p>
              <ol>
                <li>Set the <a data-link-type=3D"idl" href=3D"https://w3c.g=
ithub.io/media-source/#dom-mediasource-readystate" class=3D"internalDFN" id=
=3D"ref-for-dom-mediasource-readystate-34"><code>readyState</code></a> attr=
ibute of the <a data-link-type=3D"dfn|abstract-op" href=3D"https://w3c.gith=
ub.io/media-source/#parent-media-source" class=3D"internalDFN" id=3D"ref-fo=
r-parent-media-source-25">parent media source</a> to
                "<a data-link-type=3D"idl" href=3D"https://w3c.github.io/me=
dia-source/#dom-readystate-open" class=3D"internalDFN" id=3D"ref-for-dom-re=
adystate-open-19"><code>open</code></a>"
                </li>
                <li><a data-link-type=3D"dfn" href=3D"https://html.spec.wha=
twg.org/multipage/webappapis.html#queue-a-task">Queue a task</a> to <a data=
-link-type=3D"dfn" href=3D"https://dom.spec.whatwg.org/#concept-event-fire"=
>fire an event</a> named <a data-link-type=3D"idl" data-lt=3D"sourceopen" h=
ref=3D"https://w3c.github.io/media-source/#dfn-sourceopen" class=3D"interna=
lDFN" id=3D"ref-for-dfn-sourceopen-7"><code>sourceopen</code></a> at the <a=
 data-link-type=3D"dfn|abstract-op" href=3D"https://w3c.github.io/media-sou=
rce/#parent-media-source" class=3D"internalDFN" id=3D"ref-for-parent-media-=
source-26">parent media source</a>.
                </li>
              </ol>
            </li>
            <li>Run the <a data-link-type=3D"dfn|abstract-op" href=3D"https=
://w3c.github.io/media-source/#dfn-coded-frame-eviction" class=3D"internalD=
FN" id=3D"ref-for-dfn-coded-frame-eviction-1">coded frame eviction</a> algo=
rithm.
            </li>
            <li>
              <p>
                If the <a data-link-type=3D"attribute" data-lt=3D"[[buffer =
full flag]]" href=3D"https://w3c.github.io/media-source/#dfn-buffer-full-fl=
ag" class=3D"internalDFN" id=3D"ref-for-dfn-buffer-full-flag-2"><code>[[buf=
fer full flag]]</code></a> equals true, then throw a
                <a data-link-type=3D"interface" data-lt=3D"QuotaExceededErr=
or" href=3D"https://webidl.spec.whatwg.org/#quotaexceedederror"><code>Quota=
ExceededError</code></a> exception and abort these steps.
              </p>
              <div class=3D"note" role=3D"note" id=3D"issue-container-gener=
atedID-50"><div role=3D"heading" class=3D"note-title marker" id=3D"h-note-5=
0" aria-level=3D"5"><span>Note</span></div><p class=3D"">
                This is the signal that the implementation was unable to ev=
ict enough data to
                accommodate the append or the append is too big. The web ap=
plication <em class=3D"rfc2119">SHOULD</em> use
                <a data-link-type=3D"idl" data-lt=3D"remove()" href=3D"http=
s://w3c.github.io/media-source/#dom-sourcebuffer-remove" class=3D"internalD=
FN" id=3D"ref-for-dom-sourcebuffer-remove-4"><code>remove</code></a><code>(=
)</code> to explicitly free up space and/or reduce the size of the
                append.
              </p></div>
            </li>
          </ol>
        </section>
        <section id=3D"sourcebuffer-buffer-append"><div class=3D"header-wra=
pper"><h4 id=3D"x5-5-5-buffer-append"><bdi class=3D"secno">5.5.5 </bdi>
            <dfn id=3D"dfn-buffer-append" tabindex=3D"0" aria-haspopup=3D"d=
ialog" data-dfn-type=3D"dfn">Buffer Append</dfn>
          </h4><a class=3D"self-link" href=3D"https://w3c.github.io/media-s=
ource/#sourcebuffer-buffer-append" aria-label=3D"Permalink for Section 5.5.=
5"></a></div>
         =20
          <p>
            When <a data-link-type=3D"idl" data-lt=3D"appendBuffer()" href=
=3D"https://w3c.github.io/media-source/#dom-sourcebuffer-appendbuffer" clas=
s=3D"internalDFN" id=3D"ref-for-dom-sourcebuffer-appendbuffer-9"><code>appe=
ndBuffer</code></a><code>()</code> is called, the following steps are run t=
o process
            the appended data.
          </p>
          <ol>
            <li>Run the <a data-link-type=3D"dfn|abstract-op" href=3D"https=
://w3c.github.io/media-source/#dfn-segment-parser-loop" class=3D"internalDF=
N" id=3D"ref-for-dfn-segment-parser-loop-1">segment parser loop</a> algorit=
hm.
            </li>
            <li>If the <a data-link-type=3D"dfn|abstract-op" href=3D"https:=
//w3c.github.io/media-source/#dfn-segment-parser-loop" class=3D"internalDFN=
" id=3D"ref-for-dfn-segment-parser-loop-2">segment parser loop</a> algorith=
m in the previous step was aborted, then
            abort this algorithm.
            </li>
            <li>Set the <a data-link-type=3D"idl" href=3D"https://w3c.githu=
b.io/media-source/#dom-sourcebuffer-updating" class=3D"internalDFN" id=3D"r=
ef-for-dom-sourcebuffer-updating-21"><code>updating</code></a> attribute to=
 false.
            </li>
            <li><a data-link-type=3D"dfn" href=3D"https://html.spec.whatwg.=
org/multipage/webappapis.html#queue-a-task">Queue a task</a> to <a data-lin=
k-type=3D"dfn" href=3D"https://dom.spec.whatwg.org/#concept-event-fire">fir=
e an event</a> named <a data-link-type=3D"idl" data-lt=3D"update" href=3D"h=
ttps://w3c.github.io/media-source/#dfn-update" class=3D"internalDFN" id=3D"=
ref-for-dfn-update-2"><code>update</code></a> at this <a data-link-type=3D"=
