        <section id=3D"sourcebuffer-range-removal"><div class=3D"header-wra=
pper"><h4 id=3D"x5-5-6-range-removal"><bdi class=3D"secno">5.5.6 </bdi>
            <dfn id=3D"dfn-range-removal" tabindex=3D"0" aria-haspopup=3D"d=
ialog" data-dfn-type=3D"dfn">Range Removal</dfn>
          </h4><a class=3D"self-link" href=3D"https://w3c.github.io/media-s=
ource/#sourcebuffer-range-removal" aria-label=3D"Permalink for Section 5.5.=
6"></a></div>
         =20
          <p>
            Follow these steps when a caller needs to initiate a JavaScript=
 visible range removal
            operation that blocks other SourceBuffer updates:
          </p>
          <ol>
            <li>Let <var data-type=3D"double">start</var> equal the startin=
g <a data-link-type=3D"dfn|abstract-op" href=3D"https://w3c.github.io/media=
-source/#presentation-timestamp" class=3D"internalDFN" id=3D"ref-for-presen=
tation-timestamp-16">presentation timestamp</a> for the removal
            range, in seconds measured from <a data-link-type=3D"dfn|abstra=
ct-op" href=3D"https://w3c.github.io/media-source/#presentation-start-time"=
 class=3D"internalDFN" id=3D"ref-for-presentation-start-time-8">presentatio=
n start time</a>.
            </li>
            <li>Let <var data-type=3D"unrestricted double">end</var> equal =
the end <a data-link-type=3D"dfn|abstract-op" href=3D"https://w3c.github.io=
/media-source/#presentation-timestamp" class=3D"internalDFN" id=3D"ref-for-=
presentation-timestamp-17">presentation timestamp</a> for the
            removal range, in seconds measured from <a data-link-type=3D"df=
n|abstract-op" href=3D"https://w3c.github.io/media-source/#presentation-sta=
rt-time" class=3D"internalDFN" id=3D"ref-for-presentation-start-time-9">pre=
sentation start time</a>.
            </li>
            <li>Set the <a data-link-type=3D"idl" href=3D"https://w3c.githu=
b.io/media-source/#dom-sourcebuffer-updating" class=3D"internalDFN" id=3D"r=
ef-for-dom-sourcebuffer-updating-22"><code>updating</code></a> attribute to=
 true.
            </li>
            <li><a data-link-type=3D"dfn" href=3D"https://html.spec.whatwg.=
org/multipage/webappapis.html#queue-a-task">Queue a task</a> to <a data-lin=
k-type=3D"dfn" href=3D"https://dom.spec.whatwg.org/#concept-event-fire">fir=
e an event</a> named <a data-link-type=3D"idl" data-lt=3D"updatestart" href=
=3D"https://w3c.github.io/media-source/#dfn-updatestart" class=3D"internalD=
FN" id=3D"ref-for-dfn-updatestart-3"><code>updatestart</code></a> at this
            <a data-link-type=3D"idl" data-lt=3D"SourceBuffer" href=3D"http=
s://w3c.github.io/media-source/#dom-sourcebuffer" class=3D"internalDFN" id=
=3D"ref-for-dom-sourcebuffer-86"><code>SourceBuffer</code></a> object.
            </li>
            <li>Return control to the caller and run the rest of the steps =
asynchronously.
            </li>
            <li>Run the <a data-link-type=3D"dfn|abstract-op" href=3D"https=
://w3c.github.io/media-source/#dfn-coded-frame-removal" class=3D"internalDF=
N" id=3D"ref-for-dfn-coded-frame-removal-3">coded frame removal</a> algorit=
hm with <var data-type=3D"double">start</var> and <var data-type=3D"unrestr=
icted double">end</var> as the start and
            end of the removal range.
            </li>
            <li>Set the <a data-link-type=3D"idl" href=3D"https://w3c.githu=
b.io/media-source/#dom-sourcebuffer-updating" class=3D"internalDFN" id=3D"r=
ef-for-dom-sourcebuffer-updating-23"><code>updating</code></a> attribute to=
 false.
            </li>
            <li><a data-link-type=3D"dfn" href=3D"https://html.spec.whatwg.=
org/multipage/webappapis.html#queue-a-task">Queue a task</a> to <a data-lin=
k-type=3D"dfn" href=3D"https://dom.spec.whatwg.org/#concept-event-fire">fir=
e an event</a> named <a data-link-type=3D"idl" data-lt=3D"update" href=3D"h=
ttps://w3c.github.io/media-source/#dfn-update" class=3D"internalDFN" id=3D"=
ref-for-dfn-update-3"><code>update</code></a> at this <a data-link-type=3D"=
idl" data-lt=3D"SourceBuffer" href=3D"https://w3c.github.io/media-source/#d=
om-sourcebuffer" class=3D"internalDFN" id=3D"ref-for-dom-sourcebuffer-87"><=
code>SourceBuffer</code></a>
            object.
            </li>
            <li><a data-link-type=3D"dfn" href=3D"https://html.spec.whatwg.=
org/multipage/webappapis.html#queue-a-task">Queue a task</a> to <a data-lin=
k-type=3D"dfn" href=3D"https://dom.spec.whatwg.org/#concept-event-fire">fir=
e an event</a> named <a data-link-type=3D"idl" data-lt=3D"updateend" href=
=3D"https://w3c.github.io/media-source/#dfn-updateend" class=3D"internalDFN=
" id=3D"ref-for-dfn-updateend-6"><code>updateend</code></a> at this <a data=
-link-type=3D"idl" data-lt=3D"SourceBuffer" href=3D"https://w3c.github.io/m=
edia-source/#dom-sourcebuffer" class=3D"internalDFN" id=3D"ref-for-dom-sour=
cebuffer-88"><code>SourceBuffer</code></a>
            object.
            </li>
          </ol>
        </section>
        <section id=3D"sourcebuffer-init-segment-received"><div class=3D"he=
ader-wrapper"><h4 id=3D"x5-5-7-initialization-segment-received"><bdi class=
=3D"secno">5.5.7 </bdi>
            <dfn id=3D"dfn-initialization-segment-received" tabindex=3D"0" =
aria-haspopup=3D"dialog" data-dfn-type=3D"dfn">Initialization Segment Recei=
ved</dfn>
          </h4><a class=3D"self-link" href=3D"https://w3c.github.io/media-s=
ource/#sourcebuffer-init-segment-received" aria-label=3D"Permalink for Sect=
ion 5.5.7"></a></div>
         =20
          <p>
            The following steps are run when the <a data-link-type=3D"dfn|a=
bstract-op" href=3D"https://w3c.github.io/media-source/#dfn-segment-parser-=
loop" class=3D"internalDFN" id=3D"ref-for-dfn-segment-parser-loop-3">segmen=
t parser loop</a> successfully parses a
            complete <a data-link-type=3D"dfn|abstract-op" href=3D"https://=
w3c.github.io/media-source/#dfn-initialization-segment" class=3D"internalDF=
N" id=3D"ref-for-dfn-initialization-segment-11">initialization segment</a>:
          </p>
          <p>
            Each SourceBuffer object has a <dfn data-dfn-for=3D"SourceBuffe=
r" data-idl=3D"" data-noexport=3D"" data-dfn-type=3D"attribute" id=3D"dfn-f=
irst-initialization-segment-received-flag" tabindex=3D"0" aria-haspopup=3D"=
dialog">[[first initialization
            segment received flag]]</dfn> internal slot that tracks whether=
 the first
            <a data-link-type=3D"dfn|abstract-op" href=3D"https://w3c.githu=
b.io/media-source/#dfn-initialization-segment" class=3D"internalDFN" id=3D"=
ref-for-dfn-initialization-segment-12">initialization segment</a> has been =
appended and received by this algorithm. This flag
            is set to false when the SourceBuffer is created and updated by=
 the algorithm below.
          </p>
          <p>
            Each SourceBuffer object has a <dfn data-dfn-for=3D"SourceBuffe=
r" data-idl=3D"" data-noexport=3D"" data-dfn-type=3D"attribute" id=3D"dfn-p=
ending-initialization-segment-for-changetype-flag" tabindex=3D"0" aria-hasp=
opup=3D"dialog">[[pending
            initialization segment for changeType flag]]</dfn> internal slo=
t that tracks whether an
            <a data-link-type=3D"dfn|abstract-op" href=3D"https://w3c.githu=
b.io/media-source/#dfn-initialization-segment" class=3D"internalDFN" id=3D"=
ref-for-dfn-initialization-segment-13">initialization segment</a> is needed=
 since the most recent
            <a data-link-type=3D"idl" data-lt=3D"changeType()" href=3D"http=
s://w3c.github.io/media-source/#dom-sourcebuffer-changetype" class=3D"inter=
nalDFN" id=3D"ref-for-dom-sourcebuffer-changetype-6"><code>changeType</code=
></a><code>()</code>. This flag is set to false when the SourceBuffer is
            created, set to true by <a data-link-type=3D"idl" data-lt=3D"ch=
angeType()" href=3D"https://w3c.github.io/media-source/#dom-sourcebuffer-ch=
angetype" class=3D"internalDFN" id=3D"ref-for-dom-sourcebuffer-changetype-7=
"><code>changeType</code></a><code>()</code> and reset to false by the
            algorithm below.
          </p>
          <ol>
            <li>Update the <a data-link-type=3D"idl" href=3D"https://w3c.gi=
thub.io/media-source/#dom-mediasource-duration" class=3D"internalDFN" id=3D=
"ref-for-dom-mediasource-duration-9"><code>duration</code></a> attribute if=
 it currently equals NaN:
              <dl class=3D"switch">
                <dt>
                  If the initialization segment contains a duration:
                </dt>
                <dd>
                  Run the <a data-link-type=3D"dfn|abstract-op" href=3D"htt=
ps://w3c.github.io/media-source/#dfn-duration-change" class=3D"internalDFN"=
 id=3D"ref-for-dfn-duration-change-4">duration change</a> algorithm with <v=
ar data-type=3D"unrestricted double">new duration</var> set
                  to the duration in the initialization segment.
                </dd>
                <dt>
                  Otherwise:
                </dt>
                <dd>
                  Run the <a data-link-type=3D"dfn|abstract-op" href=3D"htt=
ps://w3c.github.io/media-source/#dfn-duration-change" class=3D"internalDFN"=
 id=3D"ref-for-dfn-duration-change-5">duration change</a> algorithm with <v=
ar data-type=3D"unrestricted double">new duration</var> set to positive
                  Infinity.
                </dd>
              </dl>
            </li>
            <li>If the <a data-link-type=3D"dfn|abstract-op" href=3D"https:=
//w3c.github.io/media-source/#dfn-initialization-segment" class=3D"internal=
DFN" id=3D"ref-for-dfn-initialization-segment-14">initialization segment</a=
> has no audio, video, or text tracks, then run the
            <a data-link-type=3D"dfn|abstract-op" href=3D"https://w3c.githu=
b.io/media-source/#dfn-append-error" class=3D"internalDFN" id=3D"ref-for-df=
n-append-error-5">append error</a> algorithm and abort these steps.
            </li>
            <li>If the <a data-link-type=3D"attribute" data-lt=3D"[[first i=
nitialization segment received flag]]" href=3D"https://w3c.github.io/media-=
source/#dfn-first-initialization-segment-received-flag" class=3D"internalDF=
N" id=3D"ref-for-dfn-first-initialization-segment-received-flag-2"><code>[[=
first initialization segment received flag]]</code></a> is true,
            then run the following steps:
              <ol>
                <li>Verify the following properties. If any of the checks f=
ail then run the
                <a data-link-type=3D"dfn|abstract-op" href=3D"https://w3c.g=
ithub.io/media-source/#dfn-append-error" class=3D"internalDFN" id=3D"ref-fo=
r-dfn-append-error-6">append error</a> algorithm and abort these steps.
                  <ul>
                    <li>The number of audio, video, and text tracks match w=
hat was in the first
                    <a data-link-type=3D"dfn|abstract-op" href=3D"https://w=
3c.github.io/media-source/#dfn-initialization-segment" class=3D"internalDFN=
" id=3D"ref-for-dfn-initialization-segment-15">initialization segment</a>.
                    </li>
                    <li>If more than one track for a single type are presen=
t (e.g., 2 audio
                    tracks), then the <a data-link-type=3D"dfn|abstract-op"=
 href=3D"https://w3c.github.io/media-source/#dfn-track-id" class=3D"interna=
lDFN" id=3D"ref-for-dfn-track-id-5">Track IDs</a> match the ones in the fir=
st <a data-link-type=3D"dfn|abstract-op" href=3D"https://w3c.github.io/medi=
a-source/#dfn-initialization-segment" class=3D"internalDFN" id=3D"ref-for-d=
fn-initialization-segment-16">initialization segment</a>.
                    </li>
                    <li>The codecs for each track are supported by the user=
 agent.
                      <div class=3D"note" role=3D"note" id=3D"issue-contain=
er-generatedID-51"><div role=3D"heading" class=3D"note-title marker" id=3D"=
h-note-51" aria-level=3D"5"><span>Note</span></div><p class=3D"">
                        User agents <em class=3D"rfc2119">MAY</em> consider=
 codecs, that would otherwise be supported, as "not
                        supported" here if the codecs were not specified in=
 <var data-type=3D"DOMString">type</var>
                        parameter passed to (a) the most recently successfu=
l
                        <a data-link-type=3D"idl" data-lt=3D"changeType()" =
href=3D"https://w3c.github.io/media-source/#dom-sourcebuffer-changetype" cl=
ass=3D"internalDFN" id=3D"ref-for-dom-sourcebuffer-changetype-8"><code>chan=
geType</code></a><code>()</code> on this <a data-link-type=3D"idl" data-lt=
=3D"SourceBuffer" href=3D"https://w3c.github.io/media-source/#dom-sourcebuf=
fer" class=3D"internalDFN" id=3D"ref-for-dom-sourcebuffer-89"><code>SourceB=
uffer</code></a> object, or (b) if no
                        successful <a data-link-type=3D"idl" data-lt=3D"cha=
ngeType()" href=3D"https://w3c.github.io/media-source/#dom-sourcebuffer-cha=
ngetype" class=3D"internalDFN" id=3D"ref-for-dom-sourcebuffer-changetype-9"=
><code>changeType</code></a><code>()</code> has yet occurred on this object=
,
                        the <a data-link-type=3D"idl" data-lt=3D"addSourceB=
uffer()" href=3D"https://w3c.github.io/media-source/#dom-mediasource-addsou=
rcebuffer" class=3D"internalDFN" id=3D"ref-for-dom-mediasource-addsourcebuf=
fer-7"><code>addSourceBuffer</code></a><code>()</code> that created this <a=
 data-link-type=3D"idl" data-lt=3D"SourceBuffer" href=3D"https://w3c.github=
.io/media-source/#dom-sourcebuffer" class=3D"internalDFN" id=3D"ref-for-dom=
-sourcebuffer-90"><code>SourceBuffer</code></a>
                        object. For example, if the most recently successfu=
l
                        <a data-link-type=3D"idl" data-lt=3D"changeType()" =
href=3D"https://w3c.github.io/media-source/#dom-sourcebuffer-changetype" cl=
ass=3D"internalDFN" id=3D"ref-for-dom-sourcebuffer-changetype-10"><code>cha=
ngeType</code></a><code>()</code> was called with <code>'video/webm'</code>=
 or
                        <code>'video/webm; codecs=3D"vp8"'</code>, and a vi=
deo track containing vp9 appears in
                        the initialization segment, then the user agent <em=
 class=3D"rfc2119">MAY</em> use this step to
                        trigger a decode error even if the other two proper=
ties' checks, above,
                        pass. Implementations are encouraged to trigger err=
or in such cases only
                        when the codec is indeed not supported or the other=
 two properties' checks
                        fail. Web authors are encouraged to use <a data-lin=
k-type=3D"idl" data-lt=3D"changeType()" href=3D"https://w3c.github.io/media=
-source/#dom-sourcebuffer-changetype" class=3D"internalDFN" id=3D"ref-for-d=
om-sourcebuffer-changetype-11"><code>changeType</code></a><code>()</code>,
                        <a data-link-type=3D"idl" data-lt=3D"addSourceBuffe=
r()" href=3D"https://w3c.github.io/media-source/#dom-mediasource-addsourceb=
uffer" class=3D"internalDFN" id=3D"ref-for-dom-mediasource-addsourcebuffer-=
8"><code>addSourceBuffer</code></a><code>()</code> and <a data-link-type=3D=
"idl" data-lt=3D"isTypeSupported()" href=3D"https://w3c.github.io/media-sou=
rce/#dom-mediasource-istypesupported" class=3D"internalDFN" id=3D"ref-for-d=
om-mediasource-istypesupported-2"><code>isTypeSupported</code></a><code>()<=
/code>
                        with precise codec parameters to more proactively d=
etect user agent
                        support. <a data-link-type=3D"idl" data-lt=3D"chang=
eType()" href=3D"https://w3c.github.io/media-source/#dom-sourcebuffer-chang=
etype" class=3D"internalDFN" id=3D"ref-for-dom-sourcebuffer-changetype-12">=
<code>changeType</code></a><code>()</code> is required if the <a data-link-=
type=3D"idl" data-lt=3D"SourceBuffer" href=3D"https://w3c.github.io/media-s=
ource/#dom-sourcebuffer" class=3D"internalDFN" id=3D"ref-for-dom-sourcebuff=
er-91"><code>SourceBuffer</code></a>
                        object's bytestream format is changing.
                      </p></div>
                    </li>
                  </ul>
                </li>
                <li>Add the appropriate <a data-link-type=3D"dfn|abstract-o=
p" href=3D"https://w3c.github.io/media-source/#dfn-track-description" class=
=3D"internalDFN" id=3D"ref-for-dfn-track-description-3">track descriptions<=
/a> from this <a data-link-type=3D"dfn|abstract-op" href=3D"https://w3c.git=
hub.io/media-source/#dfn-initialization-segment" class=3D"internalDFN" id=
=3D"ref-for-dfn-initialization-segment-17">initialization segment</a>
                to each of the <a data-link-type=3D"dfn|abstract-op" href=
=3D"https://w3c.github.io/media-source/#track-buffer" class=3D"internalDFN"=
 id=3D"ref-for-track-buffer-21">track buffers</a>.
                </li>
                <li>Set the <a data-link-type=3D"dfn|abstract-op" href=3D"h=
ttps://w3c.github.io/media-source/#need-RAP-flag" class=3D"internalDFN" id=
=3D"ref-for-need-RAP-flag-2">need random access point flag</a> on all track=
 buffers to true.
                </li>
              </ol>
            </li>
            <li>Let <var data-type=3D"boolean">active track flag</var> equa=
l false.
            </li>
            <li>
              <p>
                If the <a data-link-type=3D"attribute" data-lt=3D"[[first i=
nitialization segment received flag]]" href=3D"https://w3c.github.io/media-=
source/#dfn-first-initialization-segment-received-flag" class=3D"internalDF=
N" id=3D"ref-for-dfn-first-initialization-segment-received-flag-3"><code>[[=
first initialization segment received flag]]</code></a> is false,
                then run the following steps:
              </p>
              <ol>
                <li>If the <a data-link-type=3D"dfn|abstract-op" href=3D"ht=
tps://w3c.github.io/media-source/#dfn-initialization-segment" class=3D"inte=
rnalDFN" id=3D"ref-for-dfn-initialization-segment-18">initialization segmen=
t</a> contains tracks with codecs the user agent
                does not support, then run the <a data-link-type=3D"dfn|abs=
tract-op" href=3D"https://w3c.github.io/media-source/#dfn-append-error" cla=
ss=3D"internalDFN" id=3D"ref-for-dfn-append-error-7">append error</a> algor=
ithm and abort these steps.
                  <div class=3D"note" role=3D"note" id=3D"issue-container-g=
eneratedID-52"><div role=3D"heading" class=3D"note-title marker" id=3D"h-no=
te-52" aria-level=3D"5"><span>Note</span></div><p class=3D"">
                    User agents <em class=3D"rfc2119">MAY</em> consider cod=
ecs, that would otherwise be supported, as "not
                    supported" here if the codecs were not specified in <va=
r data-type=3D"DOMString">type</var> parameter
                    passed to (a) the most recently successful <a data-link=
-type=3D"idl" data-lt=3D"changeType()" href=3D"https://w3c.github.io/media-=
source/#dom-sourcebuffer-changetype" class=3D"internalDFN" id=3D"ref-for-do=
m-sourcebuffer-changetype-13"><code>changeType</code></a><code>()</code> on
                    this <a data-link-type=3D"idl" data-lt=3D"SourceBuffer"=
 href=3D"https://w3c.github.io/media-source/#dom-sourcebuffer" class=3D"int=
ernalDFN" id=3D"ref-for-dom-sourcebuffer-92"><code>SourceBuffer</code></a> =
object, or (b) if no successful
                    <a data-link-type=3D"idl" data-lt=3D"changeType()" href=
=3D"https://w3c.github.io/media-source/#dom-sourcebuffer-changetype" class=
=3D"internalDFN" id=3D"ref-for-dom-sourcebuffer-changetype-14"><code>change=
Type</code></a><code>()</code> has yet occurred on this object, the
                    <a data-link-type=3D"idl" data-lt=3D"addSourceBuffer()"=
 href=3D"https://w3c.github.io/media-source/#dom-mediasource-addsourcebuffe=
r" class=3D"internalDFN" id=3D"ref-for-dom-mediasource-addsourcebuffer-9"><=
code>addSourceBuffer</code></a><code>()</code> that created this <a data-li=
nk-type=3D"idl" data-lt=3D"SourceBuffer" href=3D"https://w3c.github.io/medi=
