a class=3D"internalDFN idlName" data-link-type=3D"attribute" href=3D"https:=
//w3c.github.io/media-source/#dom-managedmediasource-streaming" id=3D"ref-f=
or-dom-managedmediasource-streaming-2"><code>streaming</code></a>;</span><s=
pan data-idl=3D"" class=3D"idlAttribute" id=3D"idl-def-managedmediasource-o=
