      </section><section id=3D"algorithms"><div class=3D"header-wrapper"><h=
3 id=3D"x7-3-algorithms"><bdi class=3D"secno">7.3 </bdi>
        Algorithms
      </h3><a class=3D"self-link" href=3D"https://w3c.github.io/media-sourc=
e/#algorithms" aria-label=3D"Permalink for Section 7.3"></a></div>
      <section id=3D"managedsourcebuffer-monitoring"><div class=3D"header-w=
rapper"><h4 id=3D"x7-3-1-managedsourcebuffer-monitoring"><bdi class=3D"secn=
o">7.3.1 </bdi>
        <code>ManagedSourceBuffer</code> Monitoring
      </h4><a class=3D"self-link" href=3D"https://w3c.github.io/media-sourc=
e/#managedsourcebuffer-monitoring" aria-label=3D"Permalink for Section 7.3.=
1"></a></div>
      <p>
        The following steps are run periodically, whenever the <a data-link=
-type=3D"dfn|abstract-op" href=3D"https://w3c.github.io/media-source/#dfn-s=
ourcebuffer-monitoring" class=3D"internalDFN" id=3D"ref-for-dfn-sourcebuffe=
r-monitoring-1">SourceBuffer Monitoring</a> algorithm is scheduled to run.
      </p>
      <p>
        Having <dfn id=3D"dfn-enough-managed-data-to-ensure-uninterrupted-p=
layback" tabindex=3D"0" aria-haspopup=3D"dialog" data-dfn-type=3D"dfn">enou=
gh managed data to ensure uninterrupted playback</dfn> is an implementation
        defined condition where the user agent determines that it currently=
 has enough data to play
        the presentation without stalling for a meaningful period of time. =
This condition is
        constantly evaluated to determine when to transition the value of
        <a data-link-type=3D"idl" href=3D"https://w3c.github.io/media-sourc=
e/#dom-managedmediasource-streaming" class=3D"internalDFN" id=3D"ref-for-do=
m-managedmediasource-streaming-5"><code>streaming</code></a>. These transit=
ions indicate when the user agent believes
        it has enough data buffered or it needs more data respectively.
      </p>
      <p>
        Being <dfn id=3D"dfn-able-to-retrieve-and-buffer-data-in-an-efficie=
nt-way" tabindex=3D"0" aria-haspopup=3D"dialog" data-dfn-type=3D"dfn">able =
to retrieve and buffer data in an efficient way</dfn> is an implementation
        defined condition where the user agent determines that it can fetch=
 new data in an energy
        efficient manner while able to achieve the desired memory usage.
      </p>
      <ol class=3D"algorithm">
        <li>Run the <a data-link-type=3D"idl" data-lt=3D"MediaSource" href=
=3D"https://w3c.github.io/media-source/#dom-mediasource" class=3D"internalD=
FN" id=3D"ref-for-dom-mediasource-102"><code>MediaSource</code></a> <a data=
-link-type=3D"dfn|abstract-op" href=3D"https://w3c.github.io/media-source/#=
dfn-sourcebuffer-monitoring" class=3D"internalDFN" id=3D"ref-for-dfn-source=
buffer-monitoring-2">SourceBuffer Monitoring</a> algorithm.
        </li>
        <li>Let <var>can play uninterrupted and efficiently</var> be a flag=
 that is true if the
        <a data-link-type=3D"attribute" href=3D"https://html.spec.whatwg.or=
g/multipage/media.html#dom-media-buffered"><code>buffered</code></a> attrib=
ute contains a <a data-link-type=3D"interface" data-lt=3D"TimeRanges" href=
=3D"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/media.html#timeranges"><code>Tim=
eRanges</code></a> that includes the current
        playback position and <a data-link-type=3D"dfn|abstract-op" href=3D=
"https://w3c.github.io/media-source/#dfn-enough-managed-data-to-ensure-unin=
terrupted-playback" class=3D"internalDFN" id=3D"ref-for-dfn-enough-managed-=
data-to-ensure-uninterrupted-playback-1">enough managed data to ensure unin=
terrupted playback</a> and is
        <a data-link-type=3D"dfn|abstract-op" href=3D"https://w3c.github.io=
/media-source/#dfn-able-to-retrieve-and-buffer-data-in-an-efficient-way" cl=
ass=3D"internalDFN" id=3D"ref-for-dfn-able-to-retrieve-and-buffer-data-in-a=
n-efficient-way-1">able to retrieve and buffer data in an efficient way</a>
          <dl class=3D"switch">
            <dt>
              If <var>can play uninterrupted and efficiently</var> is not e=
qual to
              <a data-link-type=3D"idl" href=3D"https://w3c.github.io/media=
-source/#dom-managedmediasource-streaming" class=3D"internalDFN" id=3D"ref-=
for-dom-managedmediasource-streaming-6"><code>streaming</code></a>, <a data=
-link-type=3D"dfn" href=3D"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/webappapi=
s.html#queue-an-element-task">queue an element task</a> on the <a data-link=
-type=3D"dfn" href=3D"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/media.html#med=
ia-element">media element</a>
              that runs the following steps:
            </dt>
            <dd>
              <ol>
                <li>Set <a data-link-type=3D"dfn" href=3D"https://webidl.sp=
ec.whatwg.org/#this">this</a> <a data-link-type=3D"idl" href=3D"https://w3c=
.github.io/media-source/#dom-managedmediasource-streaming" class=3D"interna=
lDFN" id=3D"ref-for-dom-managedmediasource-streaming-7"><code>streaming</co=
de></a> attribute to <var>can play
                uninterrupted and efficiently</var>.
                </li>
                <li>If <var>can play uninterrupted and efficiently</var> is=
 false <a data-link-type=3D"dfn" href=3D"https://dom.spec.whatwg.org/#conce=
pt-event-fire">fire an event</a> called
                <a data-link-type=3D"idl" data-lt=3D"startstreaming" href=
=3D"https://w3c.github.io/media-source/#dfn-startstreaming" class=3D"intern=
alDFN" id=3D"ref-for-dfn-startstreaming-1"><code>startstreaming</code></a> =
at the <a data-link-type=3D"idl" data-lt=3D"ManagedMediaSource" href=3D"htt=
ps://w3c.github.io/media-source/#dom-managedmediasource" class=3D"internalD=
FN" id=3D"ref-for-dom-managedmediasource-8"><code>ManagedMediaSource</code>=
</a>.
                </li>
                <li>Otherwise, <a data-link-type=3D"dfn" href=3D"https://do=
m.spec.whatwg.org/#concept-event-fire">fire an event</a> called <a data-lin=
k-type=3D"idl" data-lt=3D"endstreaming" href=3D"https://w3c.github.io/media=
-source/#dfn-endstreaming" class=3D"internalDFN" id=3D"ref-for-dfn-endstrea=
ming-1"><code>endstreaming</code></a> at the
                <a data-link-type=3D"idl" data-lt=3D"ManagedMediaSource" hr=
ef=3D"https://w3c.github.io/media-source/#dom-managedmediasource" class=3D"=
internalDFN" id=3D"ref-for-dom-managedmediasource-9"><code>ManagedMediaSour=
ce</code></a>.
                </li>
              </ol>
            </dd>
          </dl>
        </li>
      </ol>
      </section><section id=3D"memory-cleanup"><div class=3D"header-wrapper=
"><h4 id=3D"x7-3-2-memory-cleanup"><bdi class=3D"secno">7.3.2 </bdi>
        <dfn data-dfn-for=3D"ManagedMediaSource" id=3D"dfn-memory-cleanup" =
tabindex=3D"0" aria-haspopup=3D"dialog" data-dfn-type=3D"dfn">Memory Cleanu=
p</dfn>
      </h4><a class=3D"self-link" href=3D"https://w3c.github.io/media-sourc=
e/#memory-cleanup" aria-label=3D"Permalink for Section 7.3.2"></a></div>
      <ol>
        <li>
          <dl class=3D"switch">
            <dt>
              For each <var data-type=3D"ManagedSourceBuffer">buffer</var> =
in <a data-link-type=3D"dfn" href=3D"https://webidl.spec.whatwg.org/#this">=
this</a>'s <a data-link-type=3D"idl" href=3D"https://w3c.github.io/media-so=
urce/#dom-mediasource-sourcebuffers" class=3D"internalDFN" id=3D"ref-for-do=
m-mediasource-sourcebuffers-33"><code>sourceBuffers</code></a>:
