      <section id=3D"buffered-change"><div class=3D"header-wrapper"><h4 id=
=3D"x9-3-1-buffered-change"><bdi class=3D"secno">9.3.1 </bdi>
        Buffered Change
      </h4><a class=3D"self-link" href=3D"https://w3c.github.io/media-sourc=
e/#buffered-change" aria-label=3D"Permalink for Section 9.3.1"></a></div>
      <p>
        The following steps are run at the completion of all operations to =
the
        <a data-link-type=3D"idl" data-lt=3D"ManagedSourceBuffer" href=3D"h=
ttps://w3c.github.io/media-source/#dom-managedsourcebuffer" class=3D"intern=
alDFN" id=3D"ref-for-dom-managedsourcebuffer-6"><code>ManagedSourceBuffer</=
code></a> <var data-type=3D"ManagedSourceBuffer">buffer</var> that would ca=
use a <var data-type=3D"ManagedSourceBuffer">buffer</var>'s
        <a data-link-type=3D"idl" href=3D"https://w3c.github.io/media-sourc=
e/#dom-sourcebuffer-buffered" class=3D"internalDFN" id=3D"ref-for-dom-sourc=
ebuffer-buffered-5"><code>buffered</code></a> to change. That is once <a da=
ta-link-type=3D"idl" data-lt=3D"appendBuffer()" href=3D"https://w3c.github.=
io/media-source/#dom-sourcebuffer-appendbuffer" class=3D"internalDFN" id=3D=
"ref-for-dom-sourcebuffer-appendbuffer-11"><code>appendBuffer</code></a><co=
de>()</code>,
        <a data-link-type=3D"idl" data-lt=3D"remove()" href=3D"https://w3c.=
github.io/media-source/#dom-sourcebuffer-remove" class=3D"internalDFN" id=
=3D"ref-for-dom-sourcebuffer-remove-6"><code>remove</code></a><code>()</cod=
e> or <a data-link-type=3D"dfn|abstract-op" href=3D"https://w3c.github.io/m=
edia-source/#dfn-memory-cleanup-0" class=3D"internalDFN" id=3D"ref-for-dfn-=
memory-cleanup-0-4">memory cleanup</a> algorithm have
        completed.
      </p>
      <ol>
        <li>Let <var data-type=3D"normalized TimeRanges">previous buffered =
ranges</var> equal the
        <a data-link-type=3D"idl" href=3D"https://w3c.github.io/media-sourc=
e/#dom-sourcebuffer-buffered" class=3D"internalDFN" id=3D"ref-for-dom-sourc=
ebuffer-buffered-6"><code>buffered</code></a> attribute before the changes =
occurred.
        </li>
        <li>Let <var data-type=3D"normalized TimeRanges">new buffered range=
s</var> equal the new <a data-link-type=3D"idl" href=3D"https://w3c.github.=
io/media-source/#dom-sourcebuffer-buffered" class=3D"internalDFN" id=3D"ref=
-for-dom-sourcebuffer-buffered-7"><code>buffered</code></a>
        <a data-link-type=3D"interface" data-lt=3D"TimeRanges" href=3D"http=
s://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/media.html#timeranges"><code>TimeRanges<=
/code></a>.
        </li>
        <li>Let <var data-type=3D"normalized TimeRanges">added</var> equal =
the <var data-type=3D"normalized
        TimeRanges">previous buffered ranges</var> subtracted from <var dat=
a-type=3D"normalized TimeRanges">new buffered ranges</var>.
        </li>
        <li>Let <var data-type=3D"normalized TimeRanges">removed</var> equa=
l the <var data-type=3D"normalized
        TimeRanges">new buffered ranges</var> subtracted from <var data-typ=
e=3D"normalized TimeRanges">previous buffered ranges</var>.
        </li>
        <li>Let <var>eventInitDict</var> be a new <a data-link-type=3D"idl"=
 data-lt=3D"BufferedChangeEventInit" href=3D"https://w3c.github.io/media-so=
urce/#dom-bufferedchangeeventinit" class=3D"internalDFN" id=3D"ref-for-dom-=
bufferedchangeeventinit-2"><code>BufferedChangeEventInit</code></a> diction=
ary initialized with
        <var data-type=3D"normalized TimeRanges">added</var> as its <a data=
-link-type=3D"idl" href=3D"https://w3c.github.io/media-source/#dom-buffered=
changeeventinit-addedranges" class=3D"internalDFN" id=3D"ref-for-dom-buffer=
edchangeeventinit-addedranges-1"><code>addedRanges</code></a> and <var data=
-type=3D"normalized TimeRanges">removed</var> as its
        <a data-link-type=3D"idl" href=3D"https://w3c.github.io/media-sourc=
e/#dom-bufferedchangeeventinit-removedranges" class=3D"internalDFN" id=3D"r=
ef-for-dom-bufferedchangeeventinit-removedranges-1"><code>removedRanges</co=
de></a>
        </li>
        <li><a data-link-type=3D"dfn" href=3D"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/=
multipage/webappapis.html#queue-a-task">Queue a task</a> to <a data-link-ty=
pe=3D"dfn" href=3D"https://dom.spec.whatwg.org/#concept-event-fire">fire an=
 event</a> named <a data-link-type=3D"idl" data-lt=3D"bufferedchange" href=
=3D"https://w3c.github.io/media-source/#dfn-bufferedchange" class=3D"intern=
alDFN" id=3D"ref-for-dfn-bufferedchange-3"><code>bufferedchange</code></a> =
at <var data-type=3D"ManagedSourceBuffer">buffer</var> using the
        <a data-link-type=3D"idl" data-lt=3D"BufferedChangeEvent" href=3D"h=
ttps://w3c.github.io/media-source/#dom-bufferedchangeevent" class=3D"intern=
alDFN" id=3D"ref-for-dom-bufferedchangeevent-4"><code>BufferedChangeEvent</=
code></a> interface, initialized with <var>eventInitDict</var>.
        </li>
      </ol>
      </section><section id=3D"memory-cleanup-0"><div class=3D"header-wrapp=
er"><h4 id=3D"x9-3-2-memory-cleanup"><bdi class=3D"secno">9.3.2 </bdi>
        <dfn data-dfn-for=3D"ManagedSourceBuffer" id=3D"dfn-memory-cleanup-=
0" tabindex=3D"0" aria-haspopup=3D"dialog" data-dfn-type=3D"dfn">Memory cle=
anup</dfn>
      </h4><a class=3D"self-link" href=3D"https://w3c.github.io/media-sourc=
e/#memory-cleanup-0" aria-label=3D"Permalink for Section 9.3.2"></a></div>
      <ol>
        <li>
          <dl class=3D"switch">
            <dt>
              If <a data-link-type=3D"dfn" href=3D"https://webidl.spec.what=
wg.org/#this">this</a> is not in <a data-link-type=3D"dfn" href=3D"https://=
webidl.spec.whatwg.org/#this">this</a>'s <a data-link-type=3D"idl" data-lt=
=3D"ManagedMediaSource" href=3D"https://w3c.github.io/media-source/#dom-man=
agedmediasource" class=3D"internalDFN" id=3D"ref-for-dom-managedmediasource=
-10"><code>ManagedMediaSource</code></a> parent
              <a data-link-type=3D"idl" href=3D"https://w3c.github.io/media=
-source/#dom-mediasource-activesourcebuffers" class=3D"internalDFN" id=3D"r=
ef-for-dom-mediasource-activesourcebuffers-31"><code>activeSourceBuffers</c=
ode></a>:
            </dt>
            <dd>
              <ol>
                <li>Run the <a data-link-type=3D"dfn|abstract-op" href=3D"h=
ttps://w3c.github.io/media-source/#dfn-coded-frame-removal" class=3D"intern=
alDFN" id=3D"ref-for-dfn-coded-frame-removal-6">coded frame removal</a> alg=
orithm with start set to 0, end set to
                positive infinity, and abort these steps.
                </li>
              </ol>
            </dd>
          </dl>
        </li>
        <li>Let <var data-type=3D"normalized TimeRanges">removal ranges</va=
r> equal a list of presentation time ranges
        that can be evicted from the presentation to ensure uninterrupted p=
layback from
        <a data-link-type=3D"attribute" href=3D"https://html.spec.whatwg.or=
g/multipage/media.html#dom-media-currenttime"><code>currentTime</code></a> =
until such presentation could be retrieved again.
          <div class=3D"note" role=3D"note" id=3D"issue-container-generated=
ID-84"><div role=3D"heading" class=3D"note-title marker" id=3D"h-note-84" a=
ria-level=3D"3"><span>Note</span></div><p class=3D"">
            Implementations can use different strategies for selecting <var=
 data-type=3D"normalized TimeRanges">removal ranges</var> so web
            applications shouldn't depend on a specific behavior. The web a=
pplication would listen
            to the <a data-link-type=3D"idl" data-lt=3D"bufferedchange" hre=
f=3D"https://w3c.github.io/media-source/#dfn-bufferedchange" class=3D"inter=
nalDFN" id=3D"ref-for-dfn-bufferedchange-4"><code>bufferedchange</code></a>=
 event to observe whether portions of the buffered data have
            been evicted.
          </p></div>
        </li>
        <li>For each range in <var data-type=3D"normalized TimeRanges">remo=
val ranges</var>, run the <a data-link-type=3D"dfn|abstract-op" href=3D"htt=
ps://w3c.github.io/media-source/#dfn-coded-frame-removal" class=3D"internal=
DFN" id=3D"ref-for-dfn-coded-frame-removal-7">coded frame removal</a> algor=
ithm with
        <var data-type=3D"double">start</var> and <var data-type=3D"unrestr=
icted double">end</var> equal to the removal range start and end
        timestamp respectively.
        </li>
      </ol>
    </section></section></section>
    <section id=3D"htmlmediaelement-extensions"><div class=3D"header-wrappe=
r"><h2 id=3D"x10-htmlmediaelement-extensions"><bdi class=3D"secno">10. </bd=
