ef=3D"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/media.html#htmlmediaelement"><=
code>HTMLMediaElement</code></a>'s <a data-link-type=3D"attribute" href=3D"=
https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/media.html#dom-media-buffered"><code=
>buffered</code></a> attributes on the
