=3D"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/media.html#htmlmediaelement"><co=
de>HTMLMediaElement</code></a> <em class=3D"rfc2119">MUST</em> return when =
a <a data-link-type=3D"idl" data-lt=3D"MediaSource" href=3D"https://w3c.git=
hub.io/media-source/#dom-mediasource" class=3D"internalDFN" id=3D"ref-for-d=
om-mediasource-103"><code>MediaSource</code></a> is attached to the element=
, and
