                If the <a data-link-type=3D"idl" data-lt=3D"MediaSource" hr=
ef=3D"https://w3c.github.io/media-source/#dom-mediasource" class=3D"interna=
lDFN" id=3D"ref-for-dom-mediasource-105"><code>MediaSource</code></a> was c=
onstructed in a <a data-link-type=3D"interface" data-lt=3D"Window" href=3D"=
https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/nav-history-apis.html#window"><code>=
Window</code></a>
              </dt>
              <dd>
                Set <var data-type=3D"unrestricted double">recent duration<=
/var> to be <a data-link-type=3D"idl" href=3D"https://w3c.github.io/media-s=
ource/#dom-mediasource-duration" class=3D"internalDFN" id=3D"ref-for-dom-me=
diasource-duration-13"><code>duration</code></a> and set <var>recent live s=
eekable
                range</var> to be <a data-link-type=3D"attribute" data-lt=
=3D"[[live seekable range]]" href=3D"https://w3c.github.io/media-source/#df=
n-live-seekable-range" class=3D"internalDFN" id=3D"ref-for-dfn-live-seekabl=
e-range-7"><code>[[live seekable range]]</code></a>.
              </dd>
              <dt>
