              </dt>
              <dd>
                Set <var data-type=3D"unrestricted double">recent duration<=
/var> and <var data-type=3D"normalized
          TimeRanges">recent live seekable range</var> respectively to be w=
hat the
                <a data-link-type=3D"idl" href=3D"https://w3c.github.io/med=
ia-source/#dom-mediasource-duration" class=3D"internalDFN" id=3D"ref-for-do=
m-mediasource-duration-14"><code>duration</code></a> and <a data-link-type=
=3D"attribute" data-lt=3D"[[live seekable range]]" href=3D"https://w3c.gith=
ub.io/media-source/#dfn-live-seekable-range" class=3D"internalDFN" id=3D"re=
f-for-dfn-live-seekable-range-8"><code>[[live seekable range]]</code></a> w=
ere recently,
                updated by handling implicit messages posted by the <a data=
-link-type=3D"idl" data-lt=3D"MediaSource" href=3D"https://w3c.github.io/me=
dia-source/#dom-mediasource" class=3D"internalDFN" id=3D"ref-for-dom-medias=
ource-106"><code>MediaSource</code></a> to its
                <a data-link-type=3D"attribute" data-lt=3D"[[port to main]]=
" href=3D"https://w3c.github.io/media-source/#dfn-port-to-main" class=3D"in=
ternalDFN" id=3D"ref-for-dfn-port-to-main-10"><code>[[port to main]]</code>=
</a> on every change to <a data-link-type=3D"idl" href=3D"https://w3c.githu=
b.io/media-source/#dom-mediasource-duration" class=3D"internalDFN" id=3D"re=
f-for-dom-mediasource-duration-15"><code>duration</code></a> or
                <a data-link-type=3D"attribute" data-lt=3D"[[live seekable =
