e" class=3D"internalDFN" id=3D"ref-for-dfn-live-seekable-range-9"><code>[[l=
ive seekable range]]</code></a>.
              </dd>
            </dl>
          </li>
          <li>
            <dl class=3D"switch">
              <dt>
