              <dd>
                Return an empty <a data-link-type=3D"interface" data-lt=3D"=
TimeRanges" href=3D"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/media.html#timer=
anges"><code>TimeRanges</code></a> object.
              </dd>
              <dt>
                If <var data-type=3D"unrestricted double">recent duration</=
var> equals positive Infinity:
              </dt>
              <dd>
