                      <li>Let <var data-type=3D"sequence of normalized Time=
Ranges">active ranges</var> be the ranges
                      returned by <a data-link-type=3D"idl" href=3D"https:/=
/w3c.github.io/media-source/#dom-sourcebuffer-buffered" class=3D"internalDF=
N" id=3D"ref-for-dom-sourcebuffer-buffered-8"><code>buffered</code></a> for=
 each <a data-link-type=3D"idl" data-lt=3D"SourceBuffer" href=3D"https://w3=
