nt intersection ranges</var> equal a
                      <a data-link-type=3D"interface" data-lt=3D"TimeRanges=
" href=3D"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/media.html#timeranges"><co=
de>TimeRanges</code></a> object containing a single range from 0 to <var da=
ta-type=3D"unrestricted double">highest end time</var>.
