source-activesourcebuffers-36"><code>activeSourceBuffers</code></a>.
                <div class=3D"note" role=3D"note" id=3D"issue-container-gen=
eratedID-87"><div role=3D"heading" class=3D"note-title marker" id=3D"h-note=
-87" aria-level=3D"4"><span>Note</span></div><p class=3D"">
                  The overhead of recalculating and communicating <var data=
-type=3D"normalized TimeRanges">recent intersection ranges</var> so
